9548
9549void GeneratorJavaScript::GenerateStruct(const std::shared_ptr<StructType>& s)
9550{
9551 bool first;
9552
9553 // Generate struct begin
9554 WriteLine();
9555 WriteLineIndent("/**");
9556 WriteLineIndent(" * " + *s->name + " struct");
9557 WriteLineIndent(" */");
9558 WriteIndent("class " + *s->name);
9559 if (s->base && !s->base->empty())
9560 WriteIndent(" extends " + ConvertTypeName(*s->base, false));
9561 WriteLineIndent(" {");
9562 Indent(1);
9563
9564 // Generate struct constructor
9565 if ((s->base && !s->base->empty()) || (s->body && !s->body->fields.empty()))
9566 {
9567 first = true;
9568 WriteLineIndent("/**");
9569 WriteLineIndent(" * Initialize struct");
9570 if (s->base && !s->base->empty())
9571 WriteLineIndent(" * @param {!" + ConvertTypeName(*s->base, false) + "=} parent");
9572 if (s->body)
9573 for (const auto& field : s->body->fields)
9574 WriteLineIndent(" * @param {" + std::string(field->optional ? "" : "!") + ConvertTypeName(*field) + "=} " + *field->name);
9575 WriteLineIndent(" * @constructor");
9576 WriteLineIndent(" */");
9577 WriteIndent("constructor (");
9578 if (s->base && !s->base->empty())
9579 {
9580 Write("parent = new " + ConvertTypeName(*s->base, false) + "()");
9581 first = false;
9582 }
9583 if (s->body)
9584 {
9585 for (const auto& field : s->body->fields)
9586 {
9587 Write(std::string(first ? "arg" : ", arg") + *field->name + " = " + ConvertDefault(*field));
9588 first = false;
9589 }
9590 }
9591 WriteLine(") {");
9592 Indent(1);
9593 if (s->base && !s->base->empty())
9594 {
9595 WriteLineIndent("super()");
9596 WriteLineIndent("super.copy(parent)");
9597 }
9598 if (s->body)
9599 for (const auto& field : s->body->fields)
9600 WriteLineIndent("this." + *field->name + " = arg" + *field->name);
9601 Indent(-1);
9602 WriteLineIndent("}");
9603 WriteLine();
9604 }
9605
9606 // Generate struct copy() method
9607 WriteLineIndent("/**");
9608 WriteLineIndent(" * Copy struct (shallow copy)");
9609 WriteLineIndent(" * @this {!" + *s->name + "}");
9610 WriteLineIndent(" * @param {!" + *s->name + "} other Other struct");
9611 WriteLineIndent(" * @returns {!" + *s->name + "} This struct");
9612 WriteLineIndent(" */");
9613 WriteLineIndent("copy (other) {");
9614 Indent(1);
9615 if (s->base && !s->base->empty())
9616 WriteLineIndent("super.copy(other)");
9617 if (s->body)
9618 {
9619 for (const auto& field : s->body->fields)
9620 {
9621 WriteLineIndent("if (other." + *field->name + " != null) {");
9622 Indent(1);
9623 if (field->array || field->vector || field->list)
9624 {
9625 WriteLineIndent("this." + *field->name + " = []");
9626 WriteLineIndent("for (let item of other." + *field->name + ") {");
9627 Indent(1);
9628 WriteLineIndent("if (item != null) {");
9629 Indent(1);
9630 WriteLineIndent("let tempItem");
9631 CopyValueToVariable(*field->type, "item", "tempItem", field->optional);
9632 WriteLineIndent("this." + *field->name + ".push(tempItem)");
9633 Indent(-1);
9634 WriteLineIndent("} else {");
9635 Indent(1);
9636 WriteLineIndent("this." + *field->name + ".push(undefined)");
9637 Indent(-1);
9638 WriteLineIndent("}");
9639 Indent(-1);
9640 WriteLineIndent("}");
9641 }
9642 else if (field->set)
9643 {
9644 WriteLineIndent("this." + *field->name + " = new Set()");
9645 WriteLineIndent("for (let item of other." + *field->name + ") {");
9646 Indent(1);
9647 WriteLineIndent("if (item != null) {");
9648 Indent(1);
9649 WriteLineIndent("let tempItem");
9650 CopyValueToVariable(*field->type, "item", "tempItem", field->optional);
9651 WriteLineIndent("this." + *field->name + ".add(tempItem)");
9652 Indent(-1);
9653 WriteLineIndent("} else {");
9654 Indent(1);
9655 WriteLineIndent("this." + *field->name + ".add(undefined)");
9656 Indent(-1);
9657 WriteLineIndent("}");
9658 Indent(-1);
9659 WriteLineIndent("}");
9660 }
9661 else if (field->map || field->hash)
9662 {
9663 WriteLineIndent("this." + *field->name + " = new Map()");
9664 WriteLineIndent("Object.keys(other." + *field->name + ").forEach(key => {");
9665 Indent(1);
9666 WriteLineIndent("if (key != null) {");
9667 Indent(1);
9668 WriteLineIndent("let tempKey");
9669 CopyValueToVariable(*field->key, "key", "tempKey", false);
9670 WriteLineIndent("if (other." + *field->name + "[key] != null) {");
9671 Indent(1);
9672 WriteLineIndent("let tempValue");
9673 CopyValueToVariable(*field->type, "other." + *field->name + "[key]", "tempValue", field->optional);
9674 WriteLineIndent("this." + *field->name + ".set(tempKey, tempValue)");
9675 Indent(-1);
9676 WriteLineIndent("} else {");
9677 Indent(1);
9678 WriteLineIndent("this." + *field->name + ".set(tempKey, undefined)");
9679 Indent(-1);
9680 WriteLineIndent("}");
9681 Indent(-1);
9682 WriteLineIndent("}");
9683 Indent(-1);
9684 WriteLineIndent("})");
9685 }
9686 else
9687 CopyValueToVariable(*field->type, "other." + *field->name, "this." + *field->name, field->optional);
9688 Indent(-1);
9689 WriteLineIndent("} else {");
9690 Indent(1);
9691 WriteLineIndent("this." + *field->name + " = undefined");
9692 Indent(-1);
9693 WriteLineIndent("}");
9694 }
9695 }
9696 WriteLineIndent("return this");
9697 Indent(-1);
9698 WriteLineIndent("}");
9699
9700 // Generate struct clone() method
9701 WriteLine();
9702 WriteLineIndent("/**");
9703 WriteLineIndent(" * Clone struct (deep clone)");
9704 WriteLineIndent(" * @this {!" + *s->name + "}");
9705 WriteLineIndent(" * @returns {!" + *s->name + "} Cloned struct");
9706 WriteLineIndent(" */");
9707 WriteLineIndent("clone () {");
9708 Indent(1);
9709 WriteLineIndent("// Serialize the struct to the FBE stream");
9710 WriteLineIndent("let writer = new " + *s->name + "Model(new fbe.WriteBuffer())");
9711 WriteLineIndent("writer.serialize(this)");
9712 WriteLine();
9713 WriteLineIndent("// Deserialize the struct from the FBE stream");
9714 WriteLineIndent("let reader = new " + *s->name + "Model(new fbe.ReadBuffer())");
9715 WriteLineIndent("reader.attachBuffer(writer.buffer)");
9716 WriteLineIndent("return reader.deserialize().value");
9717 Indent(-1);
9718 WriteLineIndent("}");
9719
9720 // Generate struct eq() method
9721 WriteLine();
9722 WriteLineIndent("/**");
9723 WriteLineIndent(" * Is this struct equal to other one?");
9724 WriteLineIndent(" * @this {!" + *s->name + "}");
9725 WriteLineIndent(" * @param {!" + *s->name + "} other Other struct");
9726 WriteLineIndent(" * @returns {boolean} Equal result");
9727 WriteLineIndent(" */");
9728 WriteLineIndent("eq (other) {");
9729 Indent(1);
9730 WriteLineIndent("if (!(other instanceof " + *s->name + ")) {");
9731 Indent(1);
9732 WriteLineIndent("throw new TypeError('Instance of " + *s->name + " is required!')");
9733 Indent(-1);
9734 WriteLineIndent("}");
9735 if (s->base && !s->base->empty())
9736 {
9737 WriteLineIndent("// noinspection RedundantIfStatementJS");
9738 WriteLineIndent("if (!super.eq(other)) {");
9739 Indent(1);
9740 WriteLineIndent("return false");
9741 Indent(-1);
9742 WriteLineIndent("}");
9743 }
9744 if (s->body)
9745 {
9746 for (const auto& field : s->body->fields)
9747 {
9748 if (field->keys)
9749 {
9750 WriteLineIndent("// noinspection RedundantIfStatementJS");
9751 if (IsJavaScriptType(*field->type))
9752 {
9753 WriteLineIndent("if (this." + *field->name + " !== other." + *field->name + ") {");
9754 Indent(1);
9755 WriteLineIndent("return false");
9756 Indent(-1);
9757 WriteLineIndent("}");
9758 }
9759 else
9760 {
9761 WriteLineIndent("if (this." + *field->name + " != null) {");
9762 Indent(1);
9763 WriteLineIndent("if ((other." + *field->name + " == null) || !this." + *field->name + ".eq(other." + *field->name + ")) {");
9764 Indent(1);
9765 WriteLineIndent("return false");
9766 Indent(-1);
9767 WriteLineIndent("}");
9768 Indent(-1);
9769 WriteLineIndent("} else if (other." + *field->name + " != null) {");
9770 Indent(1);
9771 WriteLineIndent("return false");
9772 Indent(-1);
9773 WriteLineIndent("}");
9774 }
9775 }
9776 }
9777 }
9778 WriteLineIndent("return true");
9779 Indent(-1);
9780 WriteLineIndent("}");
9781
9782 // Generate flags toString() method
9783 WriteLine();
9784 WriteLineIndent("/**");
9785 WriteLineIndent(" * Convert struct to string");
9786 WriteLineIndent(" * @this {!" + *s->name + "}");
9787 WriteLineIndent(" * @returns {!string} Struct value string");
9788 WriteLineIndent(" */");
9789 WriteLineIndent("toString () {");
9790 Indent(1);
9791 WriteLineIndent("let result = ''");
9792 WriteLineIndent("result += '" + *s->name + "('");
9793 first = true;
9794 if (s->base && !s->base->empty())
9795 {
9796 WriteLineIndent("result += super.toString()");
9797 first = false;
9798 }
9799 if (s->body)
9800 {
9801 for (const auto& field : s->body->fields)
9802 {
9803 WriteLineIndent("result += '" + std::string(first ? "" : ",") + *field->name + "='");
9804 if (field->attributes && field->attributes->hidden)
9805 WriteLineIndent("result += '***'");
9806 else if (field->array || field->vector)
9807 {
9808 WriteLineIndent("if (this." + *field->name + " != null) {");
9809 Indent(1);
9810 WriteLineIndent("let first = true");
9811 WriteLineIndent("result += '[' + this." + *field->name + ".length + ']['");
9812 WriteLineIndent("for (let item of this." + *field->name + ") {");
9813 Indent(1);
9814 WriteOutputStreamValue(*field->type, "item", field->optional, true);
9815 WriteLineIndent("first = false");
9816 Indent(-1);
9817 WriteLineIndent("}");
9818 WriteLineIndent("result += ']'");
9819 Indent(-1);
9820 WriteLineIndent("} else {");
9821 Indent(1);
9822 WriteLineIndent("result += '[0][]'");
9823 Indent(-1);
9824 WriteLineIndent("}");
9825 }
9826 else if (field->list)
9827 {
9828 WriteLineIndent("if (this." + *field->name + " != null) {");
9829 Indent(1);
9830 WriteLineIndent("let first = true");
9831 WriteLineIndent("result += '[' + this." + *field->name + ".length + ']<'");
9832 WriteLineIndent("for (let item of this." + *field->name + ") {");
9833 Indent(1);
9834 WriteOutputStreamValue(*field->type, "item", field->optional, true);
9835 WriteLineIndent("first = false");
9836 Indent(-1);
9837 WriteLineIndent("}");
9838 WriteLineIndent("result += '>'");
9839 Indent(-1);
9840 WriteLineIndent("} else {");
9841 Indent(1);
9842 WriteLineIndent("result += '[0]<>'");
9843 Indent(-1);
9844 WriteLineIndent("}");
9845 }
9846 else if (field->set)
9847 {
9848 WriteLineIndent("if (this." + *field->name + " != null) {");
9849 Indent(1);
9850 WriteLineIndent("let first = true");
9851 WriteLineIndent("result += '[' + this." + *field->name + ".size + ']{'");
9852 WriteLineIndent("for (let item of this." + *field->name + ") {");
9853 Indent(1);
9854 WriteOutputStreamValue(*field->type, "item", field->optional, true);
9855 WriteLineIndent("first = false");
9856 Indent(-1);
9857 WriteLineIndent("}");
9858 WriteLineIndent("result += '}'");
9859 Indent(-1);
9860 WriteLineIndent("} else {");
9861 Indent(1);
9862 WriteLineIndent("result += '[0]{}'");
9863 Indent(-1);
9864 WriteLineIndent("}");
9865 }
9866 else if (field->map)
9867 {
9868 WriteLineIndent("if (this." + *field->name + " != null) {");
9869 Indent(1);
9870 WriteLineIndent("let first = true");
9871 WriteLineIndent("result += '[' + this." + *field->name + ".size + ']<{'");
9872 WriteLineIndent("for (let [key, value] of this." + *field->name + ") {");
9873 Indent(1);
9874 WriteOutputStreamValue(*field->key, "key", false, true);
9875 WriteLineIndent("result += '->'");
9876 WriteOutputStreamValue(*field->type, "value", field->optional, false);
9877 WriteLineIndent("first = false");
9878 Indent(-1);
9879 WriteLineIndent("}");
9880 WriteLineIndent("result += '}>'");
9881 Indent(-1);
9882 WriteLineIndent("} else {");
9883 Indent(1);
9884 WriteLineIndent("result += '[0]<{}>'");
9885 Indent(-1);
9886 WriteLineIndent("}");
9887 }
9888 else if (field->hash)
9889 {
9890 WriteLineIndent("if (this." + *field->name + " != null) {");
9891 Indent(1);
9892 WriteLineIndent("let first = true");
9893 WriteLineIndent("result += '[' + this." + *field->name + ".size + '][{'");
9894 WriteLineIndent("for (let [key, value] of this." + *field->name + ") {");
9895 Indent(1);
9896 WriteOutputStreamValue(*field->key, "key", false, true);
9897 WriteLineIndent("result += '->'");
9898 WriteOutputStreamValue(*field->type, "value", field->optional, false);
9899 WriteLineIndent("first = false");
9900 Indent(-1);
9901 WriteLineIndent("}");
9902 WriteLineIndent("result += '}]'");
9903 Indent(-1);
9904 WriteLineIndent("} else {");
9905 Indent(1);
9906 WriteLineIndent("result += '[0][{}]'");
9907 Indent(-1);
9908 WriteLineIndent("}");
9909 }
9910 else
9911 WriteOutputStreamValue(*field->type, "this." + *field->name, field->optional, false);
9912 first = false;
9913 }
9914 }
9915 WriteLineIndent("result += ')'");
9916 WriteLineIndent("return result");
9917 Indent(-1);
9918 WriteLineIndent("}");
9919
9920 // Generate struct [util.inspect.custom]() method
9921 WriteLine();
9922 WriteLineIndent("/**");
9923 WriteLineIndent(" * Inspect struct");
9924 WriteLineIndent(" * @this {!" + *s->name + "}");
9925 WriteLineIndent(" * @returns {!string} Struct value string");
9926 WriteLineIndent(" */");
9927 WriteLineIndent("[util.inspect.custom] () {");
9928 Indent(1);
9929 WriteLineIndent("return this.toString()");
9930 Indent(-1);
9931 WriteLineIndent("}");
9932
9933 // Generate struct toJSON() method
9934 WriteLine();
9935 WriteLineIndent("/**");
9936 WriteLineIndent(" * Convert struct to JSON");
9937 WriteLineIndent(" * @this {!" + *s->name + "}");
9938 WriteLineIndent(" * @returns {!object} Struct value for JSON");
9939 WriteLineIndent(" */");
9940 WriteLineIndent("toJSON () {");
9941 Indent(1);
9942 if (s->base && !s->base->empty())
9943 {
9944 WriteLineIndent("let parent = super.toJSON()");
9945 WriteLineIndent("let current = {");
9946 }
9947 else
9948 WriteLineIndent("return {");
9949 Indent(1);
9950 if (s->body)
9951 {
9952 for (size_t i = 0; i < s->body->fields.size(); ++i)
9953 {
9954 bool last = (i == (s->body->fields.size() - 1));
9955 auto field = s->body->fields[i];
9956 if (field->array || field->vector || field->list || field->set)
9957 WriteLineIndent(*field->name + ": ((this." + *field->name + " != null) ? Array.from(this." + *field->name + ", item => " + ConvertVariable(*field->type, "item", field->optional) + ") : null)" + std::string(last ? "" : ","));
9958 else if (field->map || field->hash)
9959 WriteLineIndent(*field->name + ": ((this." + *field->name + " != null) ? fbe.MapToObject(new Map(Array.from(this." + *field->name + ", item => [" + ConvertVariable(*field->key, "item[0]", false) + ", " + ConvertVariable(*field->type, "item[1]", field->optional) + "]))) : null)" + std::string(last ? "" : ","));
9960 else
9961 WriteLineIndent(*field->name + ": " + ConvertVariable(*field->type, "this." + *field->name, field->optional) + std::string(last ? "" : ","));
9962
9963 }
9964 }
9965 Indent(-1);
9966 WriteLineIndent("}");
9967 if (s->base && !s->base->empty())
9968 WriteLineIndent("return { ...parent, ...current }");
9969 Indent(-1);
9970 WriteLineIndent("}");
9971
9972 // Generate struct fromJSON() method
9973 WriteLine();
9974 WriteLineIndent("/**");
9975 WriteLineIndent(" * Convert JSON to struct");
9976 WriteLineIndent(" * @param {!string} json JSON string");
9977 WriteLineIndent(" * @returns {!object} Struct value for JSON");
9978 WriteLineIndent(" */");
9979 WriteLineIndent("static fromJSON (json) {");
9980 Indent(1);
9981 WriteLineIndent("return " + *s->name + ".fromObject(JSON.parse(json))");
9982 Indent(-1);
9983 WriteLineIndent("}");
9984
9985 // Generate struct fromObject() method
9986 WriteLine();
9987 WriteLineIndent("/**");
9988 WriteLineIndent(" * Create struct from object value");
9989 WriteLineIndent(" * @param {!" + *s->name + "} other Object value");
9990 WriteLineIndent(" * @returns {!" + *s->name + "} Created struct");
9991 WriteLineIndent(" */");
9992 WriteLineIndent("static fromObject (other) {");
9993 Indent(1);
9994 WriteLineIndent("return new " + *s->name + "().copy(other)");
9995 Indent(-1);
9996 WriteLineIndent("}");
9997
9998 // Generate struct FBE type property
9999 WriteLine();
10000 WriteLineIndent("/**");
10001 WriteLineIndent(" * Get the FBE type");
10002 WriteLineIndent(" * @this {!" + *s->name + "}");
10003 WriteLineIndent(" * @returns {!number} FBE type");
10004 WriteLineIndent(" */");
10005 WriteLineIndent("get fbeType () {");
10006 Indent(1);
10007 WriteLineIndent("return " + *s->name + ".fbeType");
10008 Indent(-1);
10009 WriteLineIndent("}");
10010 WriteLine();
10011 WriteLineIndent("/**");
10012 WriteLineIndent(" * Get the FBE type (static)");
10013 WriteLineIndent(" * @this {!" + *s->name + "}");
10014 WriteLineIndent(" * @returns {!number} FBE type");
10015 WriteLineIndent(" */");
10016 WriteLineIndent("static get fbeType () {");
10017 Indent(1);
10018 if (s->base && !s->base->empty() && (s->type == 0))
10019 WriteLineIndent("return " + ConvertTypeName(*s->base, false) + ".fbeType");
10020 else
10021 WriteLineIndent("return " + std::to_string(s->type));
10022 Indent(-1);
10023 WriteLineIndent("}");
10024
10025 // Generate struct end
10026 Indent(-1);
10027 WriteLineIndent("}");
10028
10029 // Generate struct exports
10030 WriteLine();
10031 WriteLineIndent("exports." + *s->name + " = " + *s->name);
10032
10033 // Generate struct field model
10034 GenerateStructFieldModel(s);
10035
10036 // Generate struct model
10037 GenerateStructModel(s);
10038
10039 // Generate struct final models
10040 if (Final())
10041 {
10042 GenerateStructFinalModel(s);
10043 GenerateStructModelFinal(s);
10044 }
10045}
10046
10047void GeneratorJavaScript::GenerateStructFieldModel(const std::shared_ptr<StructType>& s)
10048{
10049 // Generate struct field model begin
10050 WriteLine();
10051 WriteLineIndent("/**");
10052 WriteLineIndent(" * Fast Binary Encoding " + *s->name + " field model");
10053 WriteLineIndent(" */");
10054 WriteLineIndent("class FieldModel" + *s->name + " extends fbe.FieldModel {");
10055 Indent(1);
10056
10057 // Generate struct field model constructor
10058 if ((s->base && !s->base->empty()) || (s->body && !s->body->fields.empty()))
10059 {
10060 WriteLineIndent("/**");
10061 WriteLineIndent(" * Initialize field model with the given buffer and offset");
10062 WriteLineIndent(" * @param {!fbe.ReadBuffer|!fbe.WriteBuffer} buffer Buffer");
10063 WriteLineIndent(" * @param {!number} offset Offset");
10064 WriteLineIndent(" * @constructor");
10065 WriteLineIndent(" */");
10066 WriteLineIndent("constructor (buffer, offset) {");
10067 Indent(1);
10068 WriteLineIndent("super(buffer, offset)");
10069 std::string prev_offset("4");
10070 std::string prev_size("4");
10071 if (s->base && !s->base->empty())
10072 {
10073 WriteLineIndent("this._parent = new " + ConvertTypeFieldName(*s->base, false) + "(buffer, " + prev_offset + " + " + prev_size + ")");
10074 prev_offset = "this._parent.fbeOffset";
10075 prev_size = "this._parent.fbeBody - 4 - 4";
10076 }
10077 if (s->body)
10078 {
10079 for (const auto& field : s->body->fields)
10080 {
10081 WriteLineIndent("this._" + *field->name + " = new " + ConvertTypeFieldInitialization(*field, prev_offset + " + " + prev_size, false));
10082 prev_offset = "this._" + *field->name + ".fbeOffset";
10083 prev_size = "this._" + *field->name + ".fbeSize";
10084 }
10085 }
10086 Indent(-1);
10087 WriteLineIndent("}");
10088 WriteLine();
10089 }
10090
10091 // Generate struct field model accessors
10092 if (s->base && !s->base->empty())
10093 {
10094 WriteLineIndent("/**");
10095 WriteLineIndent(" * Get the " + *s->base + " field model");
10096 WriteLineIndent(" * @this {!FieldModel" + *s->name + "}");
10097 WriteLineIndent(" * @returns {!" + ConvertTypeFieldName(*s->base, false) + "} " + *s->base + " field model");
10098 WriteLineIndent(" */");
10099 WriteLineIndent("get parent () {");
10100 Indent(1);
10101 WriteLineIndent("return this._parent");
10102 Indent(-1);
10103 WriteLineIndent("}");
10104 WriteLine();
10105 }
10106 if (s->body)
10107 {
10108 for (const auto& field : s->body->fields)
10109 {
10110 WriteLineIndent("/**");
10111 WriteLineIndent(" * Get the " + *field->name + " field model");
10112 WriteLineIndent(" * @this {!FieldModel" + *s->name + "}");
10113 WriteLineIndent(" * @returns {!" + ConvertTypeFieldDeclaration(*field, false) + "} " + *field->name + " field model");
10114 WriteLineIndent(" */");
10115 WriteLineIndent("get " + *field->name + " () {");
10116 Indent(1);
10117 WriteLineIndent("return this._" + *field->name);
10118 Indent(-1);
10119 WriteLineIndent("}");
10120 WriteLine();
10121 }
10122 }
10123
10124 // Generate struct field model FBE properties
10125 WriteLineIndent("/**");
10126 WriteLineIndent(" * Get the field size");
10127 WriteLineIndent(" * @this {!FieldModel" + *s->name + "}");
10128 WriteLineIndent(" * @returns {!number} Field size");
10129 WriteLineIndent(" */");
10130 WriteLineIndent("get fbeSize () {");
10131 Indent(1);
10132 WriteLineIndent("return 4");
10133 Indent(-1);
10134 WriteLineIndent("}");
10135 WriteLine();
10136 WriteLineIndent("/**");
10137 WriteLineIndent(" * Get the field body size");
10138 WriteLineIndent(" * @this {!FieldModel" + *s->name + "}");
10139 WriteLineIndent(" * @returns {!number} Field body size");
10140 WriteLineIndent(" */");
10141 WriteLineIndent("get fbeBody () {");
10142 Indent(1);
10143 WriteIndent("return 4 + 4");
10144 if (s->base && !s->base->empty())
10145 Write(" + this.parent.fbeBody - 4 - 4");
10146 if (s->body)
10147 for (const auto& field : s->body->fields)
10148 Write(" + this." + *field->name + ".fbeSize");
10149 WriteLine();
10150 Indent(-1);
10151 WriteLineIndent("}");
10152 WriteLine();
10153 WriteLineIndent("/**");
10154 WriteLineIndent(" * Get the field extra size");
10155 WriteLineIndent(" * @this {!FieldModel" + *s->name + "}");
10156 WriteLineIndent(" * @returns {!number} Field extra size");
10157 WriteLineIndent(" */");
10158 WriteLineIndent("get fbeExtra () {");
10159 Indent(1);
10160 WriteLineIndent("if ((this._buffer.offset + this.fbeOffset + this.fbeSize) > this._buffer.size) {");
10161 Indent(1);
10162 WriteLineIndent("return 0");
10163 Indent(-1);
10164 WriteLineIndent("}");
10165 WriteLine();
10166 WriteLineIndent("let fbeStructOffset = this.readUInt32(this.fbeOffset)");
10167 WriteLineIndent("if ((fbeStructOffset === 0) || ((this._buffer.offset + fbeStructOffset + 4) > this._buffer.size)) {");
10168 Indent(1);
10169 WriteLineIndent("return 0");
10170 Indent(-1);
10171 WriteLineIndent("}");
10172 WriteLine();
10173 WriteLineIndent("this._buffer.shift(fbeStructOffset)");
10174 WriteLine();
10175 WriteIndent("let fbeResult = this.fbeBody");
10176 Indent(1);
10177 if (s->base && !s->base->empty())
10178 Write(" + this.parent.fbeExtra");
10179 if (s->body)
10180 for (const auto& field : s->body->fields)
10181 Write(" + this." + *field->name + ".fbeExtra");
10182 WriteLine();
10183 Indent(-1);
10184 WriteLine();
10185 WriteLineIndent("this._buffer.unshift(fbeStructOffset)");
10186 WriteLine();
10187 WriteLineIndent("return fbeResult");
10188 Indent(-1);
10189 WriteLineIndent("}");
10190 WriteLine();
10191 WriteLineIndent("/**");
10192 WriteLineIndent(" * Get the field type");
10193 WriteLineIndent(" * @this {!FieldModel" + *s->name + "}");
10194 WriteLineIndent(" * @returns {!number} Field type");
10195 WriteLineIndent(" */");
10196 WriteLineIndent("get fbeType () {");
10197 Indent(1);
10198 WriteLineIndent("return FieldModel" + *s->name + ".fbeType");
10199 Indent(-1);
10200 WriteLineIndent("}");
10201 WriteLine();
10202 WriteLineIndent("/**");
10203 WriteLineIndent(" * Get the field type (static)");
10204 WriteLineIndent(" * @this {!FieldModel" + *s->name + "}");
10205 WriteLineIndent(" * @returns {!number} Field type");
10206 WriteLineIndent(" */");
10207 WriteLineIndent("static get fbeType () {");
10208 Indent(1);
10209 if (s->base && !s->base->empty() && (s->type == 0))
10210 WriteLineIndent("return " + ConvertTypeFieldName(*s->base, false) + ".fbeType");
10211 else
10212 WriteLineIndent("return " + std::to_string(s->type));
10213 Indent(-1);
10214 WriteLineIndent("}");
10215
10216 // Generate struct field model verify() method
10217 WriteLine();
10218 WriteLineIndent("/**");
10219 WriteLineIndent(" * Check if the struct value is valid");
10220 WriteLineIndent(" * @this {!FieldModel" + *s->name + "}");
10221 WriteLineIndent(" * @param {!boolean} fbeVerifyType Verify model type flag, defaults is true");
10222 WriteLineIndent(" * @returns {!boolean} Field model valid state");
10223 WriteLineIndent(" */");
10224 WriteLineIndent("verify (fbeVerifyType = true) {");
10225 Indent(1);
10226 WriteLineIndent("if ((this._buffer.offset + this.fbeOffset + this.fbeSize) > this._buffer.size) {");
10227 Indent(1);
10228 WriteLineIndent("return true");
10229 Indent(-1);
10230 WriteLineIndent("}");
10231 WriteLine();
10232 WriteLineIndent("let fbeStructOffset = this.readUInt32(this.fbeOffset)");
10233 WriteLineIndent("if ((fbeStructOffset === 0) || ((this._buffer.offset + fbeStructOffset + 4 + 4) > this._buffer.size)) {");
10234 Indent(1);
10235 WriteLineIndent("return false");
10236 Indent(-1);
10237 WriteLineIndent("}");
10238 WriteLine();
10239 WriteLineIndent("let fbeStructSize = this.readUInt32(fbeStructOffset)");
10240 WriteLineIndent("if (fbeStructSize < (4 + 4)) {");
10241 Indent(1);
10242 WriteLineIndent("return false");
10243 Indent(-1);
10244 WriteLineIndent("}");
10245 WriteLine();
10246 WriteLineIndent("let fbeStructType = this.readUInt32(fbeStructOffset + 4)");
10247 WriteLineIndent("if (fbeVerifyType && (fbeStructType !== this.fbeType)) {");
10248 Indent(1);
10249 WriteLineIndent("return false");
10250 Indent(-1);
10251 WriteLineIndent("}");
10252 WriteLine();
10253 WriteLineIndent("this._buffer.shift(fbeStructOffset)");
10254 WriteLineIndent("let fbeResult = this.verifyFields(fbeStructSize)");
10255 WriteLineIndent("this._buffer.unshift(fbeStructOffset)");
10256 WriteLineIndent("return fbeResult");
10257 Indent(-1);
10258 WriteLineIndent("}");
10259
10260 // Generate struct field model verifyFields() method
10261 WriteLine();
10262 WriteLineIndent("/**");
10263 WriteLineIndent(" * Check if the struct fields are valid");
10264 WriteLineIndent(" * @this {!FieldModel" + *s->name + "}");
10265 WriteLineIndent(" * @param {!number} fbeStructSize FBE struct size");
10266 WriteLineIndent(" * @returns {!boolean} Field model valid state");
10267 WriteLineIndent(" */");
10268 WriteLineIndent("verifyFields (fbeStructSize) {");
10269 Indent(1);
10270 if ((s->base && !s->base->empty()) || (s->body && !s->body->fields.empty()))
10271 {
10272 WriteLineIndent("let fbeCurrentSize = 4 + 4");
10273 if (s->base && !s->base->empty())
10274 {
10275 WriteLine();
10276 WriteLineIndent("if ((fbeCurrentSize + this.parent.fbeBody - 4 - 4) > fbeStructSize) {");
10277 Indent(1);
10278 WriteLineIndent("return true");
10279 Indent(-1);
10280 WriteLineIndent("}");
10281 WriteLineIndent("if (!this.parent.verifyFields(fbeStructSize)) {");
10282 Indent(1);
10283 WriteLineIndent("return false");
10284 Indent(-1);
10285 WriteLineIndent("}");
10286 WriteLineIndent("// noinspection JSUnusedAssignment");
10287 WriteLineIndent("fbeCurrentSize += this.parent.fbeBody - 4 - 4");
10288 }
10289 if (s->body)
10290 {
10291 for (const auto& field : s->body->fields)
10292 {
10293 WriteLine();
10294 WriteLineIndent("if ((fbeCurrentSize + this." + *field->name + ".fbeSize) > fbeStructSize) {");
10295 Indent(1);
10296 WriteLineIndent("return true");
10297 Indent(-1);
10298 WriteLineIndent("}");
10299 WriteLineIndent("if (!this." + *field->name + ".verify()) {");
10300 Indent(1);
10301 WriteLineIndent("return false");
10302 Indent(-1);
10303 WriteLineIndent("}");
10304 WriteLineIndent("// noinspection JSUnusedAssignment");
10305 WriteLineIndent("fbeCurrentSize += this." + *field->name + ".fbeSize");
10306 }
10307 }
10308 WriteLine();
10309 }
10310 WriteLineIndent("return true");
10311 Indent(-1);
10312 WriteLineIndent("}");
10313
10314 // Generate struct field model getBegin() method
10315 WriteLine();
10316 WriteLineIndent("/**");
10317 WriteLineIndent(" * Get the struct value (begin phase)");
10318 WriteLineIndent(" * @this {!FieldModel" + *s->name + "}");
10319 WriteLineIndent(" * @returns {!number} Field model begin offset");
10320 WriteLineIndent(" */");
10321 WriteLineIndent("getBegin () {");
10322 Indent(1);
10323 WriteLineIndent("if ((this._buffer.offset + this.fbeOffset + this.fbeSize) > this._buffer.size) {");
10324 Indent(1);
10325 WriteLineIndent("return 0");
10326 Indent(-1);
10327 WriteLineIndent("}");
10328 WriteLine();
10329 WriteLineIndent("let fbeStructOffset = this.readUInt32(this.fbeOffset)");
10330 WriteLineIndent("console.assert((fbeStructOffset > 0) && ((this._buffer.offset + fbeStructOffset + 4 + 4) <= this._buffer.size), 'Model is broken!')");
10331 WriteLineIndent("if ((fbeStructOffset === 0) || ((this._buffer.offset + fbeStructOffset + 4 + 4) > this._buffer.size)) {");
10332 Indent(1);
10333 WriteLineIndent("return 0");
10334 Indent(-1);
10335 WriteLineIndent("}");
10336 WriteLine();
10337 WriteLineIndent("let fbeStructSize = this.readUInt32(fbeStructOffset)");
10338 WriteLineIndent("console.assert((fbeStructSize >= (4 + 4)), 'Model is broken!')");
10339 WriteLineIndent("if (fbeStructSize < (4 + 4)) {");
10340 Indent(1);
10341 WriteLineIndent("return 0");
10342 Indent(-1);
10343 WriteLineIndent("}");
10344 WriteLine();
10345 WriteLineIndent("this._buffer.shift(fbeStructOffset)");
10346 WriteLineIndent("return fbeStructOffset");
10347 Indent(-1);
10348 WriteLineIndent("}");
10349
10350 // Generate struct field model getEnd() method
10351 WriteLine();
10352 WriteLineIndent("/**");
10353 WriteLineIndent(" * Get the struct value (end phase)");
10354 WriteLineIndent(" * @this {!FieldModel" + *s->name + "}");
10355 WriteLineIndent(" * @param {!number} fbeBegin Field model begin offset");
10356 WriteLineIndent(" */");
10357 WriteLineIndent("getEnd (fbeBegin) {");
10358 Indent(1);
10359 WriteLineIndent("this._buffer.unshift(fbeBegin)");
10360 Indent(-1);
10361 WriteLineIndent("}");
10362
10363 // Generate struct field model get() method
10364 WriteLine();
10365 WriteLineIndent("/**");
10366 WriteLineIndent(" * Get the struct value");
10367 WriteLineIndent(" * @this {!FieldModel" + *s->name + "}");
10368 WriteLineIndent(" * @param {!" + *s->name + "} fbeValue Default value, defaults is new " + *s->name + "()");
10369 WriteLineIndent(" * @returns {!" + *s->name + "} " + *s->name + " value");
10370 WriteLineIndent(" */");
10371 WriteLineIndent("get (fbeValue = new " + *s->name + "()) {");
10372 Indent(1);
10373 WriteLineIndent("let fbeBegin = this.getBegin()");
10374 WriteLineIndent("if (fbeBegin === 0) {");
10375 Indent(1);
10376 WriteLineIndent("return fbeValue");
10377 Indent(-1);
10378 WriteLineIndent("}");
10379 WriteLine();
10380 WriteLineIndent("let fbeStructSize = this.readUInt32(0)");
10381 WriteLineIndent("this.getFields(fbeValue, fbeStructSize)");
10382 WriteLineIndent("this.getEnd(fbeBegin)");
10383 WriteLineIndent("return fbeValue");
10384 Indent(-1);
10385 WriteLineIndent("}");
10386
10387 // Generate struct field model getFields() method
10388 WriteLine();
10389 WriteLineIndent("/**");
10390 WriteLineIndent(" * Get the struct fields values");
10391 WriteLineIndent(" * @this {!FieldModel" + *s->name + "}");
10392 WriteLineIndent(" * @param {!" + *s->name + "} fbeValue " + *s->name + " value");
10393 WriteLineIndent(" * @param {!number} fbeStructSize Struct size");
10394 WriteLineIndent(" */");
10395 WriteLineIndent("getFields (fbeValue, fbeStructSize) {");
10396 Indent(1);
10397 if ((s->base && !s->base->empty()) || (s->body && !s->body->fields.empty()))
10398 {
10399 WriteLineIndent("let fbeCurrentSize = 4 + 4");
10400 if (s->base && !s->base->empty())
10401 {
10402 WriteLine();
10403 WriteLineIndent("if ((fbeCurrentSize + this.parent.fbeBody - 4 - 4) <= fbeStructSize) {");
10404 Indent(1);
10405 WriteLineIndent("this.parent.getFields(fbeValue, fbeStructSize)");
10406 Indent(-1);
10407 WriteLineIndent("}");
10408 WriteLineIndent("// noinspection JSUnusedAssignment");
10409 WriteLineIndent("fbeCurrentSize += this.parent.fbeBody - 4 - 4");
10410 }
10411 if (s->body)
10412 {
10413 for (const auto& field : s->body->fields)
10414 {
10415 WriteLine();
10416 WriteLineIndent("if ((fbeCurrentSize + this." + *field->name + ".fbeSize) <= fbeStructSize) {");
10417 Indent(1);
10418 if (field->array || field->vector || field->list || field->set || field->map || field->hash)
10419 WriteLineIndent("this." + *field->name + ".get(fbeValue." + *field->name + ")");
10420 else
10421 WriteLineIndent("fbeValue." + *field->name + " = this." + *field->name + ".get(" + (field->value ? ConvertConstant(*field->type, *field->value, field->optional) : "") + ")");
10422 Indent(-1);
10423 WriteLineIndent("} else {");
10424 Indent(1);
10425 if (field->array || field->vector || field->list)
10426 WriteLineIndent("fbeValue." + *field->name + ".length = 0");
10427 else if (field->set || field->map || field->hash)
10428 WriteLineIndent("fbeValue." + *field->name + ".clear()");
10429 else
10430 WriteLineIndent("fbeValue." + *field->name + " = " + ConvertDefault(*field));
10431 Indent(-1);
10432 WriteLineIndent("}");
10433 WriteLineIndent("// noinspection JSUnusedAssignment");
10434 WriteLineIndent("fbeCurrentSize += this." + *field->name + ".fbeSize");
10435 }
10436 }
10437 }
10438 Indent(-1);
10439 WriteLineIndent("}");
10440
10441 // Generate struct field model setBegin() method
10442 WriteLine();
10443 WriteLineIndent("/**");
10444 WriteLineIndent(" * Set the struct value (begin phase)");
10445 WriteLineIndent(" * @this {!FieldModel" + *s->name + "}");
10446 WriteLineIndent(" * @returns {!number} Field model begin offset");
10447 WriteLineIndent(" */");
10448 WriteLineIndent("setBegin () {");
10449 Indent(1);
10450 WriteLineIndent("console.assert(((this._buffer.offset + this.fbeOffset + this.fbeSize) <= this._buffer.size), 'Model is broken!')");
10451 WriteLineIndent("if ((this._buffer.offset + this.fbeOffset + this.fbeSize) > this._buffer.size) {");
10452 Indent(1);
10453 WriteLineIndent("return 0");
10454 Indent(-1);
10455 WriteLineIndent("}");
10456 WriteLine();
10457 WriteLineIndent("let fbeStructSize = this.fbeBody");
10458 WriteLineIndent("let fbeStructOffset = this._buffer.allocate(fbeStructSize) - this._buffer.offset");
10459 WriteLineIndent("console.assert((fbeStructOffset > 0) && ((this._buffer.offset + fbeStructOffset + fbeStructSize) <= this._buffer.size), 'Model is broken!')");
10460 WriteLineIndent("if ((fbeStructOffset <= 0) || ((this._buffer.offset + fbeStructOffset + fbeStructSize) > this._buffer.size)) {");
10461 Indent(1);
10462 WriteLineIndent("return 0");
10463 Indent(-1);
10464 WriteLineIndent("}");
10465 WriteLine();
10466 WriteLineIndent("this.writeUInt32(this.fbeOffset, fbeStructOffset)");
10467 WriteLineIndent("this.writeUInt32(fbeStructOffset, fbeStructSize)");
10468 WriteLineIndent("this.writeUInt32(fbeStructOffset + 4, this.fbeType)");
10469 WriteLine();
10470 WriteLineIndent("this._buffer.shift(fbeStructOffset)");
10471 WriteLineIndent("return fbeStructOffset");
10472 Indent(-1);
10473 WriteLineIndent("}");
10474
10475 // Generate struct field model setEnd() method
10476 WriteLine();
10477 WriteLineIndent("/**");
10478 WriteLineIndent(" * Set the struct value (end phase)");
10479 WriteLineIndent(" * @this {!FieldModel" + *s->name + "}");
10480 WriteLineIndent(" * @param {!number} fbeBegin Field model begin offset");
10481 WriteLineIndent(" */");
10482 WriteLineIndent("setEnd (fbeBegin) {");
10483 Indent(1);
10484 WriteLineIndent("this._buffer.unshift(fbeBegin)");
10485 Indent(-1);
10486 WriteLineIndent("}");
10487
10488 // Generate struct field model set() method
10489 WriteLine();
10490 WriteLineIndent("/**");
10491 WriteLineIndent(" * Set the struct value");
10492 WriteLineIndent(" * @this {!FieldModel" + *s->name + "}");
10493 WriteLineIndent(" * @param {!" + *s->name + "} fbeValue " + *s->name + " value");
10494 WriteLineIndent(" */");
10495 WriteLineIndent("set (fbeValue) {");
10496 Indent(1);
10497 WriteLineIndent("let fbeBegin = this.setBegin()");
10498 WriteLineIndent("if (fbeBegin === 0) {");
10499 Indent(1);
10500 WriteLineIndent("return");
10501 Indent(-1);
10502 WriteLineIndent("}");
10503 WriteLine();
10504 WriteLineIndent("this.setFields(fbeValue)");
10505 WriteLineIndent("this.setEnd(fbeBegin)");
10506 Indent(-1);
10507 WriteLineIndent("}");
10508
10509 // Generate struct field model setFields() method
10510 WriteLine();
10511 WriteLineIndent("/**");
10512 WriteLineIndent(" * Set the struct fields values");
10513 WriteLineIndent(" * @this {!FieldModel" + *s->name + "}");
10514 WriteLineIndent(" * @param {" + *s->name + "} fbeValue " + *s->name + " value");
10515 WriteLineIndent(" */");
10516 WriteLineIndent("setFields (fbeValue) {");
10517 Indent(1);
10518 if ((s->base && !s->base->empty()) || (s->body && !s->body->fields.empty()))
10519 {
10520 if (s->base && !s->base->empty())
10521 WriteLineIndent("this.parent.setFields(fbeValue)");
10522 if (s->body)
10523 for (const auto& field : s->body->fields)
10524 WriteLineIndent("this." + *field->name + ".set(fbeValue." + *field->name + ")");
10525 }
10526 Indent(-1);
10527 WriteLineIndent("}");
10528
10529 // Generate struct field model end
10530 Indent(-1);
10531 WriteLineIndent("}");
10532
10533 // Generate struct field model exports
10534 WriteLine();
10535 WriteLineIndent("exports.FieldModel" + *s->name + " = FieldModel" + *s->name);
10536}
10537
10538void GeneratorJavaScript::GenerateStructModel(const std::shared_ptr<StructType>& s)
10539{
10540 // Generate struct model begin
10541 WriteLine();
10542 WriteLineIndent("/**");
10543 WriteLineIndent(" * Fast Binary Encoding " + *s->name + " model");
10544 WriteLineIndent(" */");
10545 WriteLineIndent("class " + *s->name + "Model extends fbe.Model {");
10546 Indent(1);
10547
10548 // Generate struct model constructor
10549 WriteLineIndent("/**");
10550 WriteLineIndent(" * Initialize model with the given buffer");
10551 WriteLineIndent(" * @param {!fbe.ReadBuffer|!fbe.WriteBuffer} buffer Read/Write buffer, defaults is new fbe.WriteBuffer()");
10552 WriteLineIndent(" * @constructor");
10553 WriteLineIndent(" */");
10554 WriteLineIndent("constructor (buffer = new fbe.WriteBuffer()) {");
10555 Indent(1);
10556 WriteLineIndent("super(buffer)");
10557 WriteLineIndent("this._model = new FieldModel" + *s->name + "(this.buffer, 4)");
10558 Indent(-1);
10559 WriteLineIndent("}");
10560
10561 // Generate struct model accessor
10562 WriteLine();
10563 WriteLineIndent("/**");
10564 WriteLineIndent(" * Get the " + *s->name + " model");
10565 WriteLineIndent(" * @this {!" + *s->name + "Model}");
10566 WriteLineIndent(" * @returns {!FieldModel" + *s->name + "} model " + *s->name + " model");
10567 WriteLineIndent(" */");
10568 WriteLineIndent("get model () {");
10569 Indent(1);
10570 WriteLineIndent("return this._model");
10571 Indent(-1);
10572 WriteLineIndent("}");
10573
10574 // Generate struct model FBE properties
10575 WriteLine();
10576 WriteLineIndent("/**");
10577 WriteLineIndent(" * Get the model size");
10578 WriteLineIndent(" * @this {!" + *s->name + "Model}");
10579 WriteLineIndent(" * @returns {!number} Model size");
10580 WriteLineIndent(" */");
10581 WriteLineIndent("get fbeSize () {");
10582 Indent(1);
10583 WriteLineIndent("return this.model.fbeSize + this.model.fbeExtra");
10584 Indent(-1);
10585 WriteLineIndent("}");
10586 WriteLine();
10587 WriteLineIndent("/**");
10588 WriteLineIndent(" * Get the model type");
10589 WriteLineIndent(" * @this {!" + *s->name + "Model}");
10590 WriteLineIndent(" * @returns {!number} Model type");
10591 WriteLineIndent(" */");
10592 WriteLineIndent("get fbeType () {");
10593 Indent(1);
10594 WriteLineIndent("return " + *s->name + "Model.fbeType");
10595 Indent(-1);
10596 WriteLineIndent("}");
10597 WriteLine();
10598 WriteLineIndent("/**");
10599 WriteLineIndent(" * Get the model type (static)");
10600 WriteLineIndent(" * @this {!" + *s->name + "Model}");
10601 WriteLineIndent(" * @returns {!number} Model type");
10602 WriteLineIndent(" */");
10603 WriteLineIndent("static get fbeType () {");
10604 Indent(1);
10605 WriteLineIndent("return FieldModel" + *s->name + ".fbeType");
10606 Indent(-1);
10607 WriteLineIndent("}");
10608
10609 // Generate struct model verify() method
10610 WriteLine();
10611 WriteLineIndent("/**");
10612 WriteLineIndent(" * Check if the struct value is valid");
10613 WriteLineIndent(" * @this {!" + *s->name + "Model}");
10614 WriteLineIndent(" * @returns {!boolean} Model valid state");
10615 WriteLineIndent(" */");
10616 WriteLineIndent("verify () {");
10617 Indent(1);
10618 WriteLineIndent("if ((this.buffer.offset + this.model.fbeOffset - 4) > this.buffer.size) {");
10619 Indent(1);
10620 WriteLineIndent("return false");
10621 Indent(-1);
10622 WriteLineIndent("}");
10623 WriteLine();
10624 WriteLineIndent("let fbeFullSize = this.readUInt32(this.model.fbeOffset - 4)");
10625 WriteLineIndent("if (fbeFullSize < this.model.fbeSize) {");
10626 Indent(1);
10627 WriteLineIndent("return false");
10628 Indent(-1);
10629 WriteLineIndent("}");
10630 WriteLine();
10631 WriteLineIndent("return this.model.verify()");
10632 Indent(-1);
10633 WriteLineIndent("}");
10634
10635 // Generate struct model createBegin() method
10636 WriteLine();
10637 WriteLineIndent("/**");
10638 WriteLineIndent(" * Create a new model (begin phase)");
10639 WriteLineIndent(" * @this {!" + *s->name + "Model}");
10640 WriteLineIndent(" * @returns {!number} Model begin offset");
10641 WriteLineIndent(" */");
10642 WriteLineIndent("createBegin () {");
10643 Indent(1);
10644 WriteLineIndent("return this.buffer.allocate(4 + this.model.fbeSize)");
10645 Indent(-1);
10646 WriteLineIndent("}");
10647
10648 // Generate struct model createEnd() method
10649 WriteLine();
10650 WriteLineIndent("/**");
10651 WriteLineIndent(" * Create a new model (end phase)");
10652 WriteLineIndent(" * @this {!" + *s->name + "Model}");
10653 WriteLineIndent(" * @param {!number} fbeBegin Model begin offset");
10654 WriteLineIndent(" */");
10655 WriteLineIndent("createEnd (fbeBegin) {");
10656 Indent(1);
10657 WriteLineIndent("let fbeEnd = this.buffer.size");
10658 WriteLineIndent("let fbeFullSize = fbeEnd - fbeBegin");
10659 WriteLineIndent("this.writeUInt32(this.model.fbeOffset - 4, fbeFullSize)");
10660 WriteLineIndent("return fbeFullSize");
10661 Indent(-1);
10662 WriteLineIndent("}");
10663
10664 // Generate struct model serialize() method
10665 WriteLine();
10666 WriteLineIndent("/**");
10667 WriteLineIndent(" * Serialize the struct value");
10668 WriteLineIndent(" * @this {!" + *s->name + "Model}");
10669 WriteLineIndent(" * @param {!" + *s->name + "} value " + *s->name + " value");
10670 WriteLineIndent(" * @return {!number} Model begin offset");
10671 WriteLineIndent(" */");
10672 WriteLineIndent("serialize (value) {");
10673 Indent(1);
10674 WriteLineIndent("let fbeBegin = this.createBegin()");
10675 WriteLineIndent("this.model.set(value)");
10676 WriteLineIndent("return this.createEnd(fbeBegin)");
10677 Indent(-1);
10678 WriteLineIndent("}");
10679
10680 // Generate struct model deserialize() methods
10681 WriteLine();
10682 WriteLineIndent("/**");
10683 WriteLineIndent(" * Deserialize the struct value");
10684 WriteLineIndent(" * @this {!" + *s->name + "Model}");
10685 WriteLineIndent(" * @param {!" + *s->name + "} value " + *s->name + " value, defaults is new " + *s->name + "()");
10686 WriteLineIndent(" * @return {!object} Deserialized " + *s->name + " value and its size");
10687 WriteLineIndent(" */");
10688 WriteLineIndent("deserialize (value = new " + *s->name + "()) {");
10689 Indent(1);
10690 WriteLineIndent("if ((this.buffer.offset + this.model.fbeOffset - 4) > this.buffer.size) {");
10691 Indent(1);
10692 WriteLineIndent("return { value: new " + *s->name + "(), size: 0 }");
10693 Indent(-1);
10694 WriteLineIndent("}");
10695 WriteLine();
10696 WriteLineIndent("let fbeFullSize = this.readUInt32(this.model.fbeOffset - 4)");
10697 WriteLineIndent("console.assert((fbeFullSize >= this.model.fbeSize), 'Model is broken!')");
10698 WriteLineIndent("if (fbeFullSize < this.model.fbeSize) {");
10699 Indent(1);
10700 WriteLineIndent("return { value: new " + *s->name + "(), size: 0 }");
10701 Indent(-1);
10702 WriteLineIndent("}");
10703 WriteLine();
10704 WriteLineIndent("this.model.get(value)");
10705 WriteLineIndent("return { value: value, size: fbeFullSize }");
10706 Indent(-1);
10707 WriteLineIndent("}");
10708
10709 // Generate struct model next() method
10710 WriteLine();
10711 WriteLineIndent("/**");
10712 WriteLineIndent(" * Move to the next struct value");
10713 WriteLineIndent(" * @this {!" + *s->name + "Model}");
10714 WriteLineIndent(" * @param {!number} prev Previous " + *s->name + " model size");
10715 WriteLineIndent(" */");
10716 WriteLineIndent("next (prev) {");
10717 Indent(1);
10718 WriteLineIndent("this.model.fbeShift(prev)");
10719 Indent(-1);
10720 WriteLineIndent("}");
10721
10722 // Generate struct model end
10723 Indent(-1);
10724 WriteLineIndent("}");
10725
10726 // Generate struct model exports
10727 WriteLine();
10728 WriteLineIndent("exports." + *s->name + "Model = " + *s->name + "Model");
10729}
10730
10731void GeneratorJavaScript::GenerateStructFinalModel(const std::shared_ptr<StructType>& s)
10732{
10733 // Generate struct final model begin
10734 WriteLine();
10735 WriteLineIndent("/**");
10736 WriteLineIndent(" * Fast Binary Encoding " + *s->name + " final model");
10737 WriteLineIndent(" */");
10738 WriteLineIndent("class FinalModel" + *s->name + " extends fbe.FinalModel {");
10739 Indent(1);
10740
10741 // Generate struct final model constructor
10742 if ((s->base && !s->base->empty()) || (s->body && !s->body->fields.empty()))
10743 {
10744 WriteLineIndent("/**");
10745 WriteLineIndent(" * Initialize final model with the given buffer and offset");
10746 WriteLineIndent(" * @param {!fbe.ReadBuffer|!fbe.WriteBuffer} buffer Buffer");
10747 WriteLineIndent(" * @param {!number} offset Offset");
10748 WriteLineIndent(" * @constructor");
10749 WriteLineIndent(" */");
10750 WriteLineIndent("constructor (buffer, offset) {");
10751 Indent(1);
10752 WriteLineIndent("super(buffer, offset)");
10753 if (s->base && !s->base->empty())
10754 WriteLineIndent("this._parent = new " + ConvertTypeFieldName(*s->base, true) + "(buffer, 0)");
10755 if (s->body)
10756 for (const auto& field : s->body->fields)
10757 WriteLineIndent("this._" + *field->name + " = new " + ConvertTypeFieldInitialization(*field, "0", true));
10758 Indent(-1);
10759 WriteLineIndent("}");
10760 WriteLine();
10761 }
10762
10763 // Generate struct final model accessors
10764 if (s->base && !s->base->empty())
10765 {
10766 WriteLineIndent("/**");
10767 WriteLineIndent(" * Get the " + *s->base + " final model");
10768 WriteLineIndent(" * @this {!FinalModel" + *s->name + "}");
10769 WriteLineIndent(" * @returns {!" + ConvertTypeFieldName(*s->base, true) + "} " + *s->base + " field model");
10770 WriteLineIndent(" */");
10771 WriteLineIndent("get parent () {");
10772 Indent(1);
10773 WriteLineIndent("return this._parent");
10774 Indent(-1);
10775 WriteLineIndent("}");
10776 WriteLine();
10777 }
10778 if (s->body)
10779 {
10780 for (const auto& field : s->body->fields)
10781 {
10782 WriteLineIndent("/**");
10783 WriteLineIndent(" * Get the " + *field->name + " final model");
10784 WriteLineIndent(" * @this {!FinalModel" + *s->name + "}");
10785 WriteLineIndent(" * @returns {!" + ConvertTypeFieldDeclaration(*field, true) + "} " + *field->name + " final model");
10786 WriteLineIndent(" */");
10787 WriteLineIndent("get " + *field->name + " () {");
10788 Indent(1);
10789 WriteLineIndent("return this._" + *field->name);
10790 Indent(-1);
10791 WriteLineIndent("}");
10792 WriteLine();
10793 }
10794 }
10795
10796 // Generate struct final model FBE properties
10797 WriteLineIndent("/**");
10798 WriteLineIndent(" * Get the allocation size");
10799 WriteLineIndent(" * @this {!FinalModel" + *s->name + "}");
10800 WriteLineIndent(" * @param {!" + *s->name + "} fbeValue " + *s->name + " value");
10801 WriteLineIndent(" * @returns {!number} Allocation size");
10802 WriteLineIndent(" */");
10803 WriteLineIndent("fbeAllocationSize (fbeValue) {");
10804 Indent(1);
10805 WriteIndent("return 0");
10806 if (s->base && !s->base->empty())
10807 Write(" + this.parent.fbeAllocationSize(fbeValue)");
10808 if (s->body)
10809 for (const auto& field : s->body->fields)
10810 Write(" + this." + *field->name + ".fbeAllocationSize(fbeValue." + *field->name + ")");
10811 WriteLine();
10812 Indent(-1);
10813 WriteLineIndent("}");
10814 WriteLine();
10815 WriteLineIndent("/**");
10816 WriteLineIndent(" * Get the final type");
10817 WriteLineIndent(" * @this {!FinalModel" + *s->name + "}");
10818 WriteLineIndent(" * @returns {!number} Final type");
10819 WriteLineIndent(" */");
10820 WriteLineIndent("get fbeType () {");
10821 Indent(1);
10822 WriteLineIndent("return FinalModel" + *s->name + ".fbeType");
10823 Indent(-1);
10824 WriteLineIndent("}");
10825 WriteLine();
10826 WriteLineIndent("/**");
10827 WriteLineIndent(" * Get the final type (static)");
10828 WriteLineIndent(" * @this {!FinalModel" + *s->name + "}");
10829 WriteLineIndent(" * @returns {!number} Final type");
10830 WriteLineIndent(" */");
10831 WriteLineIndent("static get fbeType () {");
10832 Indent(1);
10833 if (s->base && !s->base->empty() && (s->type == 0))
10834 WriteLineIndent("return " + ConvertTypeFieldName(*s->base, true) + ".fbeType");
10835 else
10836 WriteLineIndent("return " + std::to_string(s->type));
10837 Indent(-1);
10838 WriteLineIndent("}");
10839
10840 // Generate struct final model verify() method
10841 WriteLine();
10842 WriteLineIndent("/**");
10843 WriteLineIndent(" * Check if the struct value is valid");
10844 WriteLineIndent(" * @this {!FinalModel" + *s->name + "}");
10845 WriteLineIndent(" * @returns {!number} Final model size or Number.MAX_SAFE_INTEGER in case of any error");
10846 WriteLineIndent(" */");
10847 WriteLineIndent("verify () {");
10848 Indent(1);
10849 WriteLineIndent("this._buffer.shift(this.fbeOffset)");
10850 WriteLineIndent("let fbeResult = this.verifyFields()");
10851 WriteLineIndent("this._buffer.unshift(this.fbeOffset)");
10852 WriteLineIndent("return fbeResult");
10853 Indent(-1);
10854 WriteLineIndent("}");
10855
10856 // Generate struct final model verifyFields() method
10857 WriteLine();
10858 WriteLineIndent("/**");
10859 WriteLineIndent(" * Check if the struct fields are valid");
10860 WriteLineIndent(" * @this {!FinalModel" + *s->name + "}");
10861 WriteLineIndent(" * @returns {!number} Final model size or Number.MAX_SAFE_INTEGER in case of any error");
10862 WriteLineIndent(" */");
10863 WriteLineIndent("verifyFields () {");
10864 Indent(1);
10865 if ((s->base && !s->base->empty()) || (s->body && !s->body->fields.empty()))
10866 {
10867 WriteLineIndent("let fbeCurrentOffset = 0");
10868 WriteLineIndent("let fbeFieldSize");
10869 if (s->base && !s->base->empty())
10870 {
10871 WriteLine();
10872 WriteLineIndent("this.parent.fbeOffset = fbeCurrentOffset");
10873 WriteLineIndent("fbeFieldSize = this.parent.verifyFields()");
10874 WriteLineIndent("if (fbeFieldSize === Number.MAX_SAFE_INTEGER) {");
10875 Indent(1);
10876 WriteLineIndent("return Number.MAX_SAFE_INTEGER");
10877 Indent(-1);
10878 WriteLineIndent("}");
10879 WriteLineIndent("fbeCurrentOffset += fbeFieldSize");
10880 }
10881 if (s->body)
10882 {
10883 for (const auto& field : s->body->fields)
10884 {
10885 WriteLine();
10886 WriteLineIndent("this." + *field->name + ".fbeOffset = fbeCurrentOffset");
10887 WriteLineIndent("fbeFieldSize = this." + *field->name + ".verify()");
10888 WriteLineIndent("if (fbeFieldSize === Number.MAX_SAFE_INTEGER) {");
10889 Indent(1);
10890 WriteLineIndent("return Number.MAX_SAFE_INTEGER");
10891 Indent(-1);
10892 WriteLineIndent("}");
10893 WriteLineIndent("fbeCurrentOffset += fbeFieldSize");
10894 }
10895 }
10896 WriteLine();
10897 WriteLineIndent("return fbeCurrentOffset");
10898 }
10899 else
10900 WriteLineIndent("return 0");
10901 Indent(-1);
10902 WriteLineIndent("}");
10903
10904 // Generate struct final model get() method
10905 WriteLine();
10906 WriteLineIndent("/**");
10907 WriteLineIndent(" * Get the struct value");
10908 WriteLineIndent(" * @this {!FinalModel" + *s->name + "}");
10909 WriteLineIndent(" * @param {!" + *s->name + "} fbeValue " + *s->name + " value, defaults is new " + *s->name + "()");
10910 WriteLineIndent(" * @returns {!object} Result struct value and its size");
10911 WriteLineIndent(" */");
10912 WriteLineIndent("get (fbeValue = new " + *s->name + "()) {");
10913 Indent(1);
10914 WriteLineIndent("this._buffer.shift(this.fbeOffset)");
10915 WriteLineIndent("let fbeSize = this.getFields(fbeValue)");
10916 WriteLineIndent("this._buffer.unshift(this.fbeOffset)");
10917 WriteLineIndent("return { value: fbeValue, size: fbeSize }");
10918 Indent(-1);
10919 WriteLineIndent("}");
10920
10921 // Generate struct final model getFields() method
10922 WriteLine();
10923 WriteLineIndent("/**");
10924 WriteLineIndent(" * Get the struct fields values");
10925 WriteLineIndent(" * @this {!FinalModel" + *s->name + "}");
10926 WriteLineIndent(" * @param {!" + *s->name + "} fbeValue " + *s->name + " value");
10927 WriteLineIndent(" * @returns {!number} Struct size");
10928 WriteLineIndent(" */");
10929 WriteLineIndent("getFields (fbeValue) {");
10930 Indent(1);
10931 if ((s->base && !s->base->empty()) || (s->body && !s->body->fields.empty()))
10932 {
10933 WriteLineIndent("let fbeCurrentOffset = 0");
10934 WriteLineIndent("let fbeCurrentSize = 0");
10935 WriteLineIndent("let fbeResult");
10936 if (s->base && !s->base->empty())
10937 {
10938 WriteLine();
10939 WriteLineIndent("this.parent.fbeOffset = fbeCurrentOffset");
10940 WriteLineIndent("fbeResult = this.parent.getFields(fbeValue)");
10941 WriteLineIndent("// noinspection JSUnusedAssignment");
10942 WriteLineIndent("fbeCurrentOffset += fbeResult");
10943 WriteLineIndent("fbeCurrentSize += fbeResult");
10944 }
10945 if (s->body)
10946 {
10947 for (const auto& field : s->body->fields)
10948 {
10949 WriteLine();
10950 WriteLineIndent("this." + *field->name + ".fbeOffset = fbeCurrentOffset");
10951 if (field->array || field->vector || field->list || field->set || field->map || field->hash)
10952 WriteLineIndent("fbeResult = this." + *field->name + ".get(fbeValue." + *field->name + ")");
10953 else
10954 {
10955 WriteLineIndent("fbeResult = this." + *field->name + ".get()");
10956 WriteLineIndent("fbeValue." + *field->name + " = fbeResult.value");
10957 }
10958 WriteLineIndent("// noinspection JSUnusedAssignment");
10959 WriteLineIndent("fbeCurrentOffset += fbeResult.size");
10960 WriteLineIndent("fbeCurrentSize += fbeResult.size");
10961 }
10962 }
10963 WriteLine();
10964 WriteLineIndent("return fbeCurrentSize");
10965 }
10966 else
10967 WriteLineIndent("return 0");
10968 Indent(-1);
10969 WriteLineIndent("}");
10970
10971 // Generate struct final model set() method
10972 WriteLine();
10973 WriteLineIndent("/**");
10974 WriteLineIndent(" * Set the struct value");
10975 WriteLineIndent(" * @this {!FinalModel" + *s->name + "}");
10976 WriteLineIndent(" * @param {!" + *s->name + "} fbeValue " + *s->name + " value");
10977 WriteLineIndent(" * @returns {!number} Final model size");
10978 WriteLineIndent(" */");
10979 WriteLineIndent("set (fbeValue) {");
10980 Indent(1);
10981 WriteLineIndent("this._buffer.shift(this.fbeOffset)");
10982 WriteLineIndent("let fbeSize = this.setFields(fbeValue)");
10983 WriteLineIndent("this._buffer.unshift(this.fbeOffset)");
10984 WriteLineIndent("return fbeSize");
10985 Indent(-1);
10986 WriteLineIndent("}");
10987
10988 // Generate struct final model setFields() method
10989 WriteLine();
10990 WriteLineIndent("/**");
10991 WriteLineIndent(" * Set the struct fields values");
10992 WriteLineIndent(" * @this {!FinalModel" + *s->name + "}");
10993 WriteLineIndent(" * @param {" + *s->name + "} fbeValue " + *s->name + " value");
10994 WriteLineIndent(" * @returns {!number} Final model size");
10995 WriteLineIndent(" */");
10996 WriteLineIndent("setFields (fbeValue) {");
10997 Indent(1);
10998 if ((s->base && !s->base->empty()) || (s->body && !s->body->fields.empty()))
10999 {
11000 WriteLineIndent("let fbeCurrentOffset = 0");
11001 WriteLineIndent("let fbeCurrentSize = 0");
11002 WriteLineIndent("let fbeFieldSize");
11003 if (s->base && !s->base->empty())
11004 {
11005 WriteLine();
11006 WriteLineIndent("this.parent.fbeOffset = fbeCurrentOffset");
11007 WriteLineIndent("fbeFieldSize = this.parent.setFields(fbeValue)");
11008 WriteLineIndent("// noinspection JSUnusedAssignment");
11009 WriteLineIndent("fbeCurrentOffset += fbeFieldSize");
11010 WriteLineIndent("fbeCurrentSize += fbeFieldSize");
11011 }
11012 if (s->body)
11013 {
11014 for (const auto& field : s->body->fields)
11015 {
11016 WriteLine();
11017 WriteLineIndent("this." + *field->name + ".fbeOffset = fbeCurrentOffset");
11018 WriteLineIndent("fbeFieldSize = this." + *field->name + ".set(fbeValue." + *field->name + ")");
11019 WriteLineIndent("// noinspection JSUnusedAssignment");
11020 WriteLineIndent("fbeCurrentOffset += fbeFieldSize");
11021 WriteLineIndent("fbeCurrentSize += fbeFieldSize");
11022 }
11023 }
11024 WriteLine();
11025 WriteLineIndent("return fbeCurrentSize");
11026 }
11027 else
11028 WriteLineIndent("return 0");
11029 Indent(-1);
11030 WriteLineIndent("}");
11031
11032 // Generate struct final model end
11033 Indent(-1);
11034 WriteLineIndent("}");
11035
11036 // Generate struct final model exports
11037 WriteLine();
11038 WriteLineIndent("exports.FinalModel" + *s->name + " = FinalModel" + *s->name);
11039}
11040
11041void GeneratorJavaScript::GenerateStructModelFinal(const std::shared_ptr<StructType>& s)
11042{
11043 // Generate struct model final begin
11044 WriteLine();
11045 WriteLineIndent("/**");
11046 WriteLineIndent(" * Fast Binary Encoding " + *s->name + " final model");
11047 WriteLineIndent(" */");
11048 WriteLineIndent("class " + *s->name + "FinalModel extends fbe.Model {");
11049 Indent(1);
11050
11051 // Generate struct model final constructor
11052 WriteLineIndent("/**");
11053 WriteLineIndent(" * Initialize final model with the given buffer");
11054 WriteLineIndent(" * @param {!fbe.ReadBuffer|!fbe.WriteBuffer} buffer Read/Write buffer, defaults is new fbe.WriteBuffer()");
11055 WriteLineIndent(" * @constructor");
11056 WriteLineIndent(" */");
11057 WriteLineIndent("constructor (buffer = new fbe.WriteBuffer()) {");
11058 Indent(1);
11059 WriteLineIndent("super(buffer)");
11060 WriteLineIndent("this._model = new FinalModel" + *s->name + "(this.buffer, 8)");
11061 Indent(-1);
11062 WriteLineIndent("}");
11063
11064 // Generate struct model final FBE properties
11065 WriteLine();
11066 WriteLineIndent("/**");
11067 WriteLineIndent(" * Get the model type");
11068 WriteLineIndent(" * @this {!" + *s->name + "FinalModel}");
11069 WriteLineIndent(" * @returns {!number} Model type");
11070 WriteLineIndent(" */");
11071 WriteLineIndent("get fbeType () {");
11072 Indent(1);
11073 WriteLineIndent("return " + *s->name + "FinalModel.fbeType");
11074 Indent(-1);
11075 WriteLineIndent("}");
11076 WriteLine();
11077 WriteLineIndent("/**");
11078 WriteLineIndent(" * Get the model type (static)");
11079 WriteLineIndent(" * @this {!" + *s->name + "FinalModel}");
11080 WriteLineIndent(" * @returns {!number} Model type");
11081 WriteLineIndent(" */");
11082 WriteLineIndent("static get fbeType () {");
11083 Indent(1);
11084 WriteLineIndent("return FinalModel" + *s->name + ".fbeType");
11085 Indent(-1);
11086 WriteLineIndent("}");
11087
11088 // Generate struct model final verify() method
11089 WriteLine();
11090 WriteLineIndent("/**");
11091 WriteLineIndent(" * Check if the struct value is valid");
11092 WriteLineIndent(" * @this {!" + *s->name + "FinalModel}");
11093 WriteLineIndent(" * @returns {!boolean} Model valid state");
11094 WriteLineIndent(" */");
11095 WriteLineIndent("verify () {");
11096 Indent(1);
11097 WriteLineIndent("if ((this.buffer.offset + this._model.fbeOffset) > this.buffer.size) {");
11098 Indent(1);
11099 WriteLineIndent("return false");
11100 Indent(-1);
11101 WriteLineIndent("}");
11102 WriteLine();
11103 WriteLineIndent("let fbeStructSize = this.readUInt32(this._model.fbeOffset - 8)");
11104 WriteLineIndent("let fbeStructType = this.readUInt32(this._model.fbeOffset - 4)");
11105 WriteLineIndent("if ((fbeStructSize <= 0) || (fbeStructType !== this.fbeType)) {");
11106 Indent(1);
11107 WriteLineIndent("return false");
11108 Indent(-1);
11109 WriteLineIndent("}");
11110 WriteLine();
11111 WriteLineIndent("return ((8 + this._model.verify()) === fbeStructSize)");
11112 Indent(-1);
11113 WriteLineIndent("}");
11114
11115 // Generate struct model final serialize() method
11116 WriteLine();
11117 WriteLineIndent("/**");
11118 WriteLineIndent(" * Serialize the struct value");
11119 WriteLineIndent(" * @this {!" + *s->name + "FinalModel}");
11120 WriteLineIndent(" * @param {!" + *s->name + "} value " + *s->name + " value");
11121 WriteLineIndent(" * @return {!number} Struct size");
11122 WriteLineIndent(" */");
11123 WriteLineIndent("serialize (value) {");
11124 Indent(1);
11125 WriteLineIndent("let fbeInitialSize = this.buffer.size");
11126 WriteLine();
11127 WriteLineIndent("let fbeStructType = this.fbeType");
11128 WriteLineIndent("let fbeStructSize = 8 + this._model.fbeAllocationSize(value)");
11129 WriteLineIndent("let fbeStructOffset = this.buffer.allocate(fbeStructSize) - this.buffer.offset");
11130 WriteLineIndent("console.assert(((this.buffer.offset + fbeStructOffset + fbeStructSize) <= this.buffer.size), 'Model is broken!')");
11131 WriteLineIndent("if ((this.buffer.offset + fbeStructOffset + fbeStructSize) > this.buffer.size) {");
11132 Indent(1);
11133 WriteLineIndent("return 0");
11134 Indent(-1);
11135 WriteLineIndent("}");
11136 WriteLine();
11137 WriteLineIndent("fbeStructSize = 8 + this._model.set(value)");
11138 WriteLineIndent("this.buffer.resize(fbeInitialSize + fbeStructSize)");
11139 WriteLine();
11140 WriteLineIndent("this.writeUInt32(this._model.fbeOffset - 8, fbeStructSize)");
11141 WriteLineIndent("this.writeUInt32(this._model.fbeOffset - 4, fbeStructType)");
11142 WriteLine();
11143 WriteLineIndent("return fbeStructSize");
11144 Indent(-1);
11145 WriteLineIndent("}");
11146
11147 // Generate struct model final deserialize() methods
11148 WriteLine();
11149 WriteLineIndent("/**");
11150 WriteLineIndent(" * Deserialize the struct value");
11151 WriteLineIndent(" * @this {!" + *s->name + "FinalModel}");
11152 WriteLineIndent(" * @param {!" + *s->name + "} value " + *s->name + " value, defaults is new " + *s->name + "()");
11153 WriteLineIndent(" * @return {!object} Deserialized " + *s->name + " value and its size");
11154 WriteLineIndent(" */");
11155 WriteLineIndent("deserialize (value = new " + *s->name + "()) {");
11156 Indent(1);
11157 WriteLineIndent("console.assert(((this.buffer.offset + this._model.fbeOffset) <= this.buffer.size), 'Model is broken!')");
11158 WriteLineIndent("if ((this.buffer.offset + this._model.fbeOffset) > this.buffer.size) {");
11159 Indent(1);
11160 WriteLineIndent("return { value: new " + *s->name + "(), size: 0 }");
11161 Indent(-1);
11162 WriteLineIndent("}");
11163 WriteLine();
11164 WriteLineIndent("let fbeStructSize = this.readUInt32(this._model.fbeOffset - 8)");
11165 WriteLineIndent("let fbeStructType = this.readUInt32(this._model.fbeOffset - 4)");
11166 WriteLineIndent("console.assert(((fbeStructSize > 0) && (fbeStructType === this.fbeType)), 'Model is broken!')");
11167 WriteLineIndent("if ((fbeStructSize <= 0) || (fbeStructType !== this.fbeType)) {");
11168 Indent(1);
11169 WriteLineIndent("return { value: new " + *s->name + "(), size: 8 }");
11170 Indent(-1);
11171 WriteLineIndent("}");
11172 WriteLine();
11173 WriteLineIndent("let fbeResult = this._model.get(value)");
11174 WriteLineIndent("return { value: fbeResult.value, size: (8 + fbeResult.size) }");
11175 Indent(-1);
11176 WriteLineIndent("}");
11177
11178 // Generate struct model final next() method
11179 WriteLine();
11180 WriteLineIndent("/**");
11181 WriteLineIndent(" * Move to the next struct value");
11182 WriteLineIndent(" * @this {!" + *s->name + "FinalModel}");
11183 WriteLineIndent(" * @param {!number} prev Previous " + *s->name + " model size");
11184 WriteLineIndent(" */");
11185 WriteLineIndent("next (prev) {");
11186 Indent(1);
11187 WriteLineIndent("this._model.fbeShift(prev)");
11188 Indent(-1);
11189 WriteLineIndent("}");
11190
11191 // Generate struct model final end
11192 Indent(-1);
11193 WriteLineIndent("}");
11194
11195 // Generate struct model final exports
11196 WriteLine();
11197 WriteLineIndent("exports." + *s->name + "FinalModel = " + *s->name + "FinalModel");
11198}
