11200void GeneratorJavaScript::GenerateProtocolVersion(const std::shared_ptr<Package>& p)
11201{
11202 // Generate protocol version constants
11203 WriteLine();
11204 WriteLineIndent("// Protocol major version");
11205 WriteLineIndent("const ProtocolVersionMajor = " + std::to_string(p->version->major));
11206 WriteLineIndent("// Protocol minor version");
11207 WriteLineIndent("const ProtocolVersionMinor = " + std::to_string(p->version->minor));
11208
11209 // Generate sender exports
11210 WriteLine();
11211 WriteLineIndent("exports.ProtocolVersionMajor = ProtocolVersionMajor");
11212 WriteLineIndent("exports.ProtocolVersionMinor = ProtocolVersionMinor");
11213}
11214
11215void GeneratorJavaScript::GenerateSender(const std::shared_ptr<Package>& p, bool final)
11216{
11217 std::string sender = (final ? "FinalSender" : "Sender");
11218 std::string model = (final ? "FinalModel" : "Model");
11219
11220 // Generate sender begin
11221 WriteLine();
11222 WriteLineIndent("/**");
11223 if (final)
11224 WriteLineIndent(" * Fast Binary Encoding " + *p->name + " final sender");
11225 else
11226 WriteLineIndent(" * Fast Binary Encoding " + *p->name + " sender");
11227 WriteLineIndent(" */");
11228 WriteLineIndent("class " + sender + " extends fbe.Sender {");
11229 Indent(1);
11230
11231 // Generate sender constructor
11232 WriteLineIndent("/**");
11233 WriteLineIndent(" * Initialize " + *p->name + " sender with the given buffer");
11234 WriteLineIndent(" * @param {!fbe.WriteBuffer} buffer Write buffer, defaults is new fbe.WriteBuffer()");
11235 WriteLineIndent(" * @constructor");
11236 WriteLineIndent(" */");
11237 WriteLineIndent("constructor (buffer = new fbe.WriteBuffer()) {");
11238 Indent(1);
11239 WriteLineIndent("super(buffer, " + std::string(final ? "true" : "false") + ")");
11240 if (p->import)
11241 {
11242 for (const auto& import : p->import->imports)
11243 WriteLineIndent("this._" + *import + "Sender = new " + *import + "." + sender + "(this.buffer)");
11244 }
11245 if (p->body)
11246 {
11247 for (const auto& s : p->body->structs)
11248 if (s->message)
11249 WriteLineIndent("this._" + *s->name + "Model = new " + *s->name + "" + model + "(this.buffer)");
11250 }
11251 WriteLineIndent("this.onSendHandler = this.onSend");
11252 WriteLineIndent("this.onSendLogHandler = this.onSendLog");
11253 Indent(-1);
11254 WriteLineIndent("}");
11255
11256 // Generate imported senders accessors
11257 if (p->import)
11258 {
11259 WriteLine();
11260 WriteLineIndent("// Imported senders");
11261 for (const auto& import : p->import->imports)
11262 {
11263 WriteLine();
11264 WriteLineIndent("/**");
11265 WriteLineIndent(" * Get imported " + *import + " sender");
11266 WriteLineIndent(" * @this {!" + sender + "}");
11267 WriteLineIndent(" * @returns {!" + *import + "." + sender + "} " + *import + " sender");
11268 WriteLineIndent(" */");
11269 WriteLineIndent("get " + *import + "Sender () {");
11270 Indent(1);
11271 WriteLineIndent("return this._" + *import + "Sender");
11272 Indent(-1);
11273 WriteLineIndent("}");
11274 }
11275 }
11276
11277 // Generate sender models accessors
11278 if (p->body)
11279 {
11280 WriteLine();
11281 WriteLineIndent("// Sender models accessors");
11282 for (const auto& s : p->body->structs)
11283 {
11284 if (s->message)
11285 {
11286 WriteLine();
11287 WriteLineIndent("/**");
11288 WriteLineIndent(" * Get " + *s->name + " model");
11289 WriteLineIndent(" * @this {!" + sender + "}");
11290 WriteLineIndent(" * @returns {!" + *s->name + "Model} " + *s->name + " model");
11291 WriteLineIndent(" */");
11292 WriteLineIndent("get " + *s->name + "Model () {");
11293 Indent(1);
11294 WriteLineIndent("return this._" + *s->name + "Model");
11295 Indent(-1);
11296 WriteLineIndent("}");
11297 }
11298 }
11299 }
11300
11301 // Generate sender methods
11302 WriteLine();
11303 WriteLineIndent("// Send methods");
11304 WriteLine();
11305 WriteLineIndent("/**");
11306 WriteLineIndent(" * Send value");
11307 WriteLineIndent(" * @this {!" + sender + "}");
11308 WriteLineIndent(" * @param {!object} value Value to send");
11309 WriteLineIndent(" * @returns {!number} Sent bytes");
11310 WriteLineIndent(" */");
11311 WriteLineIndent("send (value) {");
11312 Indent(1);
11313 if (p->body)
11314 {
11315 for (const auto& s : p->body->structs)
11316 {
11317 if (s->message)
11318 {
11319 WriteLineIndent("if ((value instanceof " + *s->name + ") && (value.fbeType === this." + *s->name + "Model.fbeType)) {");
11320 Indent(1);
11321 WriteLineIndent("return this.send_" + *s->name + "(value)");
11322 Indent(-1);
11323 WriteLineIndent("}");
11324 }
11325 }
11326 }
11327 if (p->import)
11328 {
11329 WriteLineIndent("let result = 0");
11330 for (const auto& import : p->import->imports)
11331 {
11332 WriteLineIndent("result = this._" + *import + "Sender.send(value)");
11333 WriteLineIndent("if (result > 0) {");
11334 Indent(1);
11335 WriteLineIndent("return result");
11336 Indent(-1);
11337 WriteLineIndent("}");
11338 }
11339 }
11340 WriteLineIndent("return 0");
11341 Indent(-1);
11342 WriteLineIndent("}");
11343 if (p->body)
11344 {
11345 for (const auto& s : p->body->structs)
11346 {
11347 if (s->message)
11348 {
11349 WriteLine();
11350 WriteLineIndent("/**");
11351 WriteLineIndent(" * Send " + *s->name + " value");
11352 WriteLineIndent(" * @this {!" + sender + "}");
11353 WriteLineIndent(" * @param {!" + *s->name + "} value " + *s->name + " value to send");
11354 WriteLineIndent(" * @returns {!number} Sent bytes");
11355 WriteLineIndent(" */");
11356 WriteLineIndent("send_" + *s->name + " (value) { // eslint-disable-line");
11357 Indent(1);
11358 WriteLineIndent("// Serialize the value into the FBE stream");
11359 WriteLineIndent("let serialized = this." + *s->name + "Model.serialize(value)");
11360 WriteLineIndent("console.assert((serialized > 0), '" + *p->name + "." + *s->name + " serialization failed!')");
11361 WriteLineIndent("console.assert(this." + *s->name + "Model.verify(), '" + *p->name + "." + *s->name + " validation failed!')");
11362 WriteLine();
11363 WriteLineIndent("// Log the value");
11364 WriteLineIndent("if (this.logging) {");
11365 Indent(1);
11366 WriteLineIndent("this.onSendLog(value.toString())");
11367 Indent(-1);
11368 WriteLineIndent("}");
11369 WriteLine();
11370 WriteLineIndent("// Send the serialized value");
11371 WriteLineIndent("return this.sendSerialized(serialized)");
11372 Indent(-1);
11373 WriteLineIndent("}");
11374 }
11375 }
11376 }
11377
11378 // Generate sender message handler
11379 WriteLine();
11380 WriteLineIndent("/**");
11381 WriteLineIndent(" * Send message handler");
11382 WriteLineIndent(" * @this {!" + sender + "}");
11383 WriteLineIndent(" * @param {!Uint8Array} buffer Buffer to send");
11384 WriteLineIndent(" * @param {!number} offset Buffer offset");
11385 WriteLineIndent(" * @param {!number} size Buffer size");
11386 WriteLineIndent(" */");
11387 WriteLineIndent("onSend (buffer, offset, size) {");
11388 Indent(1);
11389 WriteLineIndent("console.assert(true, '" + *p->name + ".Sender.onSend() not implemented!')");
11390 WriteLineIndent("debugger // eslint-disable-line");
11391 WriteLineIndent("return 0");
11392 Indent(-1);
11393 WriteLineIndent("}");
11394
11395 // Generate setup send message handler
11396 WriteLine();
11397 WriteLineIndent("/**");
11398 WriteLineIndent(" * Setup send message handler");
11399 WriteLineIndent(" * @this {!" + sender + "}");
11400 WriteLineIndent(" * @param {!function} handler Send message handler");
11401 WriteLineIndent(" */");
11402 WriteLineIndent("set onSendHandler (handler) { // eslint-disable-line");
11403 Indent(1);
11404 WriteLineIndent("this.onSend = handler");
11405 if (p->import)
11406 {
11407 for (const auto& import : p->import->imports)
11408 WriteLineIndent("this._" + *import + "Sender.onSendHandler = handler");
11409 }
11410 Indent(-1);
11411 WriteLineIndent("}");
11412
11413 // Generate setup send log message handler
11414 WriteLine();
11415 WriteLineIndent("/**");
11416 WriteLineIndent(" * Setup send log message handler");
11417 WriteLineIndent(" * @this {!" + sender + "}");
11418 WriteLineIndent(" * @param {!function} handler Send log message handler");
11419 WriteLineIndent(" */");
11420 WriteLineIndent("set onSendLogHandler (handler) { // eslint-disable-line");
11421 Indent(1);
11422 WriteLineIndent("this.onSendLog = handler");
11423 if (p->import)
11424 {
11425 for (const auto& import : p->import->imports)
11426 WriteLineIndent("this._" + *import + "Sender.onSendLogHandler = handler");
11427 }
11428 Indent(-1);
11429 WriteLineIndent("}");
11430
11431 // Generate sender end
11432 Indent(-1);
11433 WriteLineIndent("}");
11434
11435 // Generate sender exports
11436 WriteLine();
11437 WriteLineIndent("exports." + sender + " = " + sender);
11438}
11439
11440void GeneratorJavaScript::GenerateReceiver(const std::shared_ptr<Package>& p, bool final)
11441{
11442 std::string receiver = (final ? "FinalReceiver" : "Receiver");
11443 std::string model = (final ? "FinalModel" : "Model");
11444
11445 // Generate receiver begin
11446 WriteLine();
11447 WriteLineIndent("/**");
11448 if (final)
11449 WriteLineIndent(" * Fast Binary Encoding " + *p->name + " final receiver");
11450 else
11451 WriteLineIndent(" * Fast Binary Encoding " + *p->name + " receiver");
11452 WriteLineIndent(" */");
11453 WriteLineIndent("class " + receiver + " extends fbe.Receiver {");
11454 Indent(1);
11455
11456 // Generate receiver constructor
11457 WriteLineIndent("/**");
11458 WriteLineIndent(" * Initialize " + *p->name + " receiver with the given buffer");
11459 WriteLineIndent(" * @param {!fbe.WriteBuffer} buffer Write buffer, defaults is new WriteBuffer()");
11460 WriteLineIndent(" * @constructor");
11461 WriteLineIndent(" */");
11462 WriteLineIndent("constructor (buffer = new fbe.WriteBuffer()) {");
11463 Indent(1);
11464 WriteLineIndent("super(buffer, " + std::string(final ? "true" : "false") + ")");
11465 if (p->import)
11466 {
11467 for (const auto& import : p->import->imports)
11468 WriteLineIndent("this._" + *import + "Receiver = new " + *import + "." + receiver + "(this.buffer)");
11469 }
11470 if (p->body)
11471 {
11472 for (const auto& s : p->body->structs)
11473 {
11474 if (s->message)
11475 {
11476 WriteLineIndent("this._" + *s->name + "Value = new " + *s->name + "()");
11477 WriteLineIndent("this._" + *s->name + "Model = new " + *s->name + model + "()");
11478 }
11479 }
11480 }
11481 WriteLineIndent("this.onReceiveLogHandler = this.onReceiveLog");
11482 Indent(-1);
11483 WriteLineIndent("}");
11484
11485 // Generate imported receiver accessors
11486 if (p->import)
11487 {
11488 WriteLine();
11489 WriteLineIndent("// Imported receivers");
11490 for (const auto& import : p->import->imports)
11491 {
11492 WriteLine();
11493 WriteLineIndent("/**");
11494 WriteLineIndent(" * Get imported " + *import + " receiver");
11495 WriteLineIndent(" * @this {!" + receiver + "}");
11496 WriteLineIndent(" * @returns {" + receiver + "} " + *import + " receiver");
11497 WriteLineIndent(" */");
11498 WriteLineIndent("get " + *import + "Receiver () {");
11499 Indent(1);
11500 WriteLineIndent("return this._" + *import + "Receiver");
11501 Indent(-1);
11502 WriteLineIndent("}");
11503 WriteLine();
11504 WriteLineIndent("/**");
11505 WriteLineIndent(" * Set imported " + *import + " receiver");
11506 WriteLineIndent(" * @this {!" + receiver + "}");
11507 WriteLineIndent(" * @param {" + receiver + "} receiver " + *import + " receiver");
11508 WriteLineIndent(" */");
11509 WriteLineIndent("set " + *import + "Receiver (receiver) {");
11510 Indent(1);
11511 WriteLineIndent("this._" + *import + "Receiver = receiver");
11512 Indent(-1);
11513 WriteLineIndent("}");
11514 }
11515 }
11516
11517 // Generate receiver handlers
11518 if (p->body)
11519 {
11520 WriteLine();
11521 WriteLineIndent("// Receive handlers");
11522 for (const auto& s : p->body->structs)
11523 {
11524 if (s->message)
11525 {
11526 WriteLine();
11527 WriteLineIndent("/**");
11528 WriteLineIndent(" * " + *s->name + " receive handler");
11529 WriteLineIndent(" * @this {!" + receiver + "}");
11530 WriteLineIndent(" * @param {!" + *s->name + "} value " + *s->name + " received value");
11531 WriteLineIndent(" */");
11532 WriteLineIndent("onReceive_" + *s->name + " (value) {} // eslint-disable-line");
11533 }
11534 }
11535 WriteLine();
11536 }
11537
11538 // Generate receiver message handler
11539 WriteLineIndent("/**");
11540 WriteLineIndent(" * " + *p->name + " receive message handler");
11541 WriteLineIndent(" * @this {!" + receiver + "}");
11542 WriteLineIndent(" * @param {!number} type Message type");
11543 WriteLineIndent(" * @param {!Uint8Array} buffer Buffer to send");
11544 WriteLineIndent(" * @param {!number} offset Buffer offset");
11545 WriteLineIndent(" * @param {!number} size Buffer size");
11546 WriteLineIndent(" * @returns {!boolean} Success flag");
11547 WriteLineIndent(" */");
11548 WriteLineIndent("onReceive (type, buffer, offset, size) {");
11549 Indent(1);
11550 if (p->body)
11551 {
11552 WriteLineIndent("switch (type) {");
11553 Indent(1);
11554 for (const auto& s : p->body->structs)
11555 {
11556 if (s->message)
11557 {
11558 WriteLineIndent("case " + *s->name + model + ".fbeType: {");
11559 Indent(1);
11560 WriteLineIndent("// Deserialize the value from the FBE stream");
11561 WriteLineIndent("this._" + *s->name + "Model.attachBuffer(buffer, offset)");
11562 WriteLineIndent("console.assert(this._" + *s->name + "Model.verify(), '" + *p->name + "." + *s->name + " validation failed!')");
11563 WriteLineIndent("let deserialized = this._" + *s->name + "Model.deserialize(this._" + *s->name + "Value)");
11564 WriteLineIndent("console.assert((deserialized.size > 0), '" + *p->name + "." + *s->name + " deserialization failed!')");
11565 WriteLine();
11566 WriteLineIndent("// Log the value");
11567 WriteLineIndent("if (this.logging) {");
11568 Indent(1);
11569 WriteLineIndent("this.onReceiveLog(this._" + *s->name + "Value.toString())");
11570 Indent(-1);
11571 WriteLineIndent("}");
11572 WriteLine();
11573 WriteLineIndent("// Call receive handler with deserialized value");
11574 WriteLineIndent("this.onReceive_" + *s->name + "(this._" + *s->name + "Value)");
11575 WriteLineIndent("return true");
11576 Indent(-1);
11577 WriteLineIndent("}");
11578 }
11579 }
11580 WriteLineIndent("default: break");
11581 Indent(-1);
11582 WriteLineIndent("}");
11583 }
11584 if (p->import)
11585 {
11586 WriteLine();
11587 for (const auto& import : p->import->imports)
11588 {
11589 WriteLineIndent("// noinspection RedundantIfStatementJS");
11590 WriteLineIndent("if ((this." + *import + "Receiver != null) && this." + *import + "Receiver.onReceive(type, buffer, offset, size)) {");
11591 Indent(1);
11592 WriteLineIndent("return true");
11593 Indent(-1);
11594 WriteLineIndent("}");
11595 }
11596 WriteLine();
11597 }
11598 WriteLineIndent("return false");
11599 Indent(-1);
11600 WriteLineIndent("}");
11601
11602 // Generate setup receive log message handler
11603 WriteLine();
11604 WriteLineIndent("/**");
11605 WriteLineIndent(" * Setup receive log message handler");
11606 WriteLineIndent(" * @this {!" + receiver + "}");
11607 WriteLineIndent(" * @param {!function} handler Receive log message handler");
11608 WriteLineIndent(" */");
11609 WriteLineIndent("set onReceiveLogHandler (handler) { // eslint-disable-line");
11610 Indent(1);
11611 WriteLineIndent("this.onReceiveLog = handler");
11612 if (p->import)
11613 {
11614 for (const auto& import : p->import->imports)
11615 WriteLineIndent("this._" + *import + "Receiver.onReceiveLogHandler = handler");
11616 }
11617 Indent(-1);
11618 WriteLineIndent("}");
11619
11620 // Generate receiver end
11621 Indent(-1);
11622 WriteLineIndent("}");
11623
11624 // Generate receiver exports
11625 WriteLine();
11626 WriteLineIndent("exports." + receiver + " = " + receiver + "");
11627}
11628
11629void GeneratorJavaScript::GenerateProxy(const std::shared_ptr<Package>& p, bool final)
11630{
11631 std::string proxy = (final ? "FinalProxy" : "Proxy");
11632 std::string model = (final ? "FinalModel" : "Model");
11633
11634 // Generate proxy begin
11635 WriteLine();
11636 WriteLineIndent("/**");
11637 if (final)
11638 WriteLineIndent(" * Fast Binary Encoding " + *p->name + " final proxy");
11639 else
11640 WriteLineIndent(" * Fast Binary Encoding " + *p->name + " proxy");
11641 WriteLineIndent(" */");
11642 WriteLineIndent("class " + proxy + " extends fbe.Receiver {");
11643 Indent(1);
11644
11645 // Generate proxy constructor
11646 WriteLineIndent("/**");
11647 WriteLineIndent(" * Initialize " + *p->name + " proxy with the given buffer");
11648 WriteLineIndent(" * @param {!fbe.WriteBuffer} buffer Write buffer, defaults is new WriteBuffer()");
11649 WriteLineIndent(" * @constructor");
11650 WriteLineIndent(" */");
11651 WriteLineIndent("constructor (buffer = new fbe.WriteBuffer()) {");
11652 Indent(1);
11653 WriteLineIndent("super(buffer, " + std::string(final ? "true" : "false") + ")");
11654 if (p->import)
11655 {
11656 for (const auto& import : p->import->imports)
11657 WriteLineIndent("this._" + *import + "Proxy = new " + *import + "." + proxy + "(this.buffer)");
11658 }
11659 if (p->body)
11660 {
11661 for (const auto& s : p->body->structs)
11662 if (s->message)
11663 WriteLineIndent("this._" + *s->name + "Model = new " + *s->name + model + "()");
11664 }
11665 Indent(-1);
11666 WriteLineIndent("}");
11667
11668 // Generate imported proxy accessors
11669 if (p->import)
11670 {
11671 WriteLine();
11672 WriteLineIndent("// Imported proxy");
11673 for (const auto& import : p->import->imports)
11674 {
11675 WriteLine();
11676 WriteLineIndent("/**");
11677 WriteLineIndent(" * Get imported " + *import + " proxy");
11678 WriteLineIndent(" * @this {!" + proxy + "}");
11679 WriteLineIndent(" * @returns {" + proxy + "} " + *import + " proxy");
11680 WriteLineIndent(" */");
11681 WriteLineIndent("get " + *import + "Proxy () {");
11682 Indent(1);
11683 WriteLineIndent("return this._" + *import + "Proxy");
11684 Indent(-1);
11685 WriteLineIndent("}");
11686 WriteLine();
11687 WriteLineIndent("/**");
11688 WriteLineIndent(" * Set imported " + *import + " proxy");
11689 WriteLineIndent(" * @this {!" + proxy + "}");
11690 WriteLineIndent(" * @param {" + proxy + "} proxy " + *import + " proxy");
11691 WriteLineIndent(" */");
11692 WriteLineIndent("set " + *import + "Proxy (proxy) {");
11693 Indent(1);
11694 WriteLineIndent("this._" + *import + "Proxy = proxy");
11695 Indent(-1);
11696 WriteLineIndent("}");
11697 }
11698 }
11699
11700 // Generate proxy handlers
11701 if (p->body)
11702 {
11703 WriteLine();
11704 WriteLineIndent("// Proxy handlers");
11705 for (const auto& s : p->body->structs)
11706 {
11707 if (s->message)
11708 {
11709 WriteLine();
11710 WriteLineIndent("/**");
11711 WriteLineIndent(" * " + *s->name + " proxy handler");
11712 WriteLineIndent(" * @this {!" + proxy + "}");
11713 WriteLineIndent(" * @param {!" + *s->name + "} model " + *s->name + " model");
11714 WriteLineIndent(" * @param {!number} type Message type");
11715 WriteLineIndent(" * @param {!Uint8Array} buffer Buffer to send");
11716 WriteLineIndent(" * @param {!number} offset Buffer offset");
11717 WriteLineIndent(" * @param {!number} size Buffer size");
11718 WriteLineIndent(" */");
11719 WriteLineIndent("onProxy_" + *s->name + " (model, type, buffer, offset, size) {} // eslint-disable-line");
11720 }
11721 }
11722 WriteLine();
11723 }
11724
11725 // Generate proxy message handler
11726 WriteLineIndent("/**");
11727 WriteLineIndent(" * " + *p->name + " receive message handler");
11728 WriteLineIndent(" * @this {!" + proxy + "}");
11729 WriteLineIndent(" * @param {!number} type Message type");
11730 WriteLineIndent(" * @param {!Uint8Array} buffer Buffer to send");
11731 WriteLineIndent(" * @param {!number} offset Buffer offset");
11732 WriteLineIndent(" * @param {!number} size Buffer size");
11733 WriteLineIndent(" * @returns {!boolean} Success flag");
11734 WriteLineIndent(" */");
11735 WriteLineIndent("onReceive (type, buffer, offset, size) {");
11736 Indent(1);
11737 if (p->body)
11738 {
11739 WriteLineIndent("switch (type) {");
11740 Indent(1);
11741 for (const auto& s : p->body->structs)
11742 {
11743 if (s->message)
11744 {
11745 WriteLineIndent("case " + *s->name + model + ".fbeType: {");
11746 Indent(1);
11747 WriteLineIndent("// Attach the FBE stream to the proxy model");
11748 WriteLineIndent("this._" + *s->name + "Model.attachBuffer(buffer, offset)");
11749 WriteLineIndent("console.assert(this._" + *s->name + "Model.verify(), '" + *p->name + "." + *s->name + " validation failed!')");
11750 WriteLine();
11751 WriteLineIndent("let fbeBegin = this._" + *s->name + "Model.model.getBegin()");
11752 WriteLineIndent("if (fbeBegin === 0) {");
11753 Indent(1);
11754 WriteLineIndent("return false");
11755 Indent(-1);
11756 WriteLineIndent("}");
11757 WriteLineIndent("// Call proxy handler");
11758 WriteLineIndent("this.onProxy_" + *s->name + "(this._" + *s->name + "Model, type, buffer, offset, size)");
11759 WriteLineIndent("this._" + *s->name + "Model.model.getEnd(fbeBegin)");
11760 WriteLineIndent("return true");
11761 Indent(-1);
11762 WriteLineIndent("}");
11763 }
11764 }
11765 WriteLineIndent("default: break");
11766 Indent(-1);
11767 WriteLineIndent("}");
11768 }
11769 if (p->import)
11770 {
11771 WriteLine();
11772 for (const auto& import : p->import->imports)
11773 {
11774 WriteLineIndent("// noinspection RedundantIfStatementJS");
11775 WriteLineIndent("if ((this." + *import + "Proxy != null) && this." + *import + "Proxy.onReceive(type, buffer, offset, size)) {");
11776 Indent(1);
11777 WriteLineIndent("return true");
11778 Indent(-1);
11779 WriteLineIndent("}");
11780 }
11781 WriteLine();
11782 }
11783 WriteLineIndent("return false");
11784 Indent(-1);
11785 WriteLineIndent("}");
11786
11787 // Generate proxy end
11788 Indent(-1);
11789 WriteLineIndent("}");
11790
11791 // Generate proxy exports
11792 WriteLine();
11793 WriteLineIndent("exports." + proxy + " = " + proxy + "");
11794}
11795
11796void GeneratorJavaScript::GenerateClient(const std::shared_ptr<Package>& p, bool final)
11797{
11798 std::string client = (final ? "FinalClient" : "Client");
11799 std::string model = (final ? "FinalModel" : "Model");
11800
11801 // Generate client begin
11802 WriteLine();
11803 WriteLineIndent("/**");
11804 if (final)
11805 WriteLineIndent(" * Fast Binary Encoding " + *p->name + " final client");
11806 else
11807 WriteLineIndent(" * Fast Binary Encoding " + *p->name + " client");
11808 WriteLineIndent(" */");
11809 WriteLineIndent("class " + client + " extends fbe.Client {");
11810 Indent(1);
11811
11812 // Generate sender constructor
11813 WriteLineIndent("/**");
11814 WriteLineIndent(" * Initialize " + *p->name + " client with the given buffers");
11815 WriteLineIndent(" * @param {!fbe.WriteBuffer} sendBuffer Send buffer, defaults is new fbe.WriteBuffer()");
11816 WriteLineIndent(" * @param {!fbe.WriteBuffer} receiveBuffer Receive buffer, defaults is new fbe.WriteBuffer()");
11817 WriteLineIndent(" * @constructor");
11818 WriteLineIndent(" */");
11819 WriteLineIndent("constructor (sendBuffer = new fbe.WriteBuffer(), receiveBuffer = new fbe.WriteBuffer()) {");
11820 Indent(1);
11821 WriteLineIndent("super(sendBuffer, receiveBuffer, " + std::string(final ? "true" : "false") + ")");
11822 if (p->import)
11823 {
11824 for (const auto& import : p->import->imports)
11825 WriteLineIndent("this._" + *import + "Client = new " + *import + "." + client + "(this.sendBuffer, this.receiveBuffer)");
11826 }
11827 if (p->body)
11828 {
11829 for (const auto& s : p->body->structs)
11830 {
11831 if (s->message)
11832 {
11833 WriteLineIndent("this._" + *s->name + "SenderModel = new " + *s->name + "" + model + "(this.sendBuffer)");
11834 WriteLineIndent("this._" + *s->name + "ReceiverValue = new " + *s->name + "()");
11835 WriteLineIndent("this._" + *s->name + "ReceiverModel = new " + *s->name + model + "()");
11836 }
11837 }
11838 }
11839 WriteLineIndent("this.onSendHandler = this.onSend");
11840 WriteLineIndent("this.onSendLogHandler = this.onSendLog");
11841 WriteLineIndent("this.onReceiveLogHandler = this.onReceiveLog");
11842 WriteLineIndent("this._timestamp = 0");
11843 WriteLineIndent("this._requests_by_id = new Map()");
11844 WriteLineIndent("this._requests_by_timestamp = new Map()");
11845 Indent(-1);
11846 WriteLineIndent("}");
11847
11848 // Generate imported clients accessors
11849 if (p->import)
11850 {
11851 WriteLine();
11852 WriteLineIndent("// Imported clients");
11853 for (const auto& import : p->import->imports)
11854 {
11855 WriteLine();
11856 WriteLineIndent("/**");
11857 WriteLineIndent(" * Get imported " + *import + " client");
11858 WriteLineIndent(" * @this {!" + client + "}");
11859 WriteLineIndent(" * @returns {!" + *import + "." + client + "} " + *import + " client");
11860 WriteLineIndent(" */");
11861 WriteLineIndent("get " + *import + "Client () {");
11862 Indent(1);
11863 WriteLineIndent("return this._" + *import + "Client");
11864 Indent(-1);
11865 WriteLineIndent("}");
11866 }
11867 }
11868
11869 // Generate sender models accessors
11870 if (p->body)
11871 {
11872 WriteLine();
11873 WriteLineIndent("// Sender models accessors");
11874 for (const auto& s : p->body->structs)
11875 {
11876 if (s->message)
11877 {
11878 WriteLine();
11879 WriteLineIndent("/**");
11880 WriteLineIndent(" * Get " + *s->name + " model");
11881 WriteLineIndent(" * @this {!" + client + "}");
11882 WriteLineIndent(" * @returns {!" + *s->name + "Model} " + *s->name + " sender model");
11883 WriteLineIndent(" */");
11884 WriteLineIndent("get " + *s->name + "SenderModel () {");
11885 Indent(1);
11886 WriteLineIndent("return this._" + *s->name + "SenderModel");
11887 Indent(-1);
11888 WriteLineIndent("}");
11889 }
11890 }
11891 }
11892
11893 // Generate reset and watchdog methods
11894 WriteLine();
11895 WriteLineIndent("// Reset and watchdog methods");
11896 WriteLine();
11897 WriteLineIndent("/**");
11898 WriteLineIndent(" * Reset the client");
11899 WriteLineIndent(" * @this {!" + client + "}");
11900 WriteLineIndent(" */");
11901 WriteLineIndent("reset () {");
11902 Indent(1);
11903 WriteLineIndent("super.reset()");
11904 WriteLineIndent("this.resetRequests()");
11905 Indent(-1);
11906 WriteLineIndent("}");
11907 WriteLine();
11908 WriteLineIndent("/**");
11909 WriteLineIndent(" * Watchdog for timeouts");
11910 WriteLineIndent(" * @this {!" + client + "}");
11911 WriteLineIndent(" * @param {!number} utc UTC timestamp");
11912 WriteLineIndent(" */");
11913 WriteLineIndent("watchdog (utc) {");
11914 Indent(1);
11915 WriteLineIndent("this.watchdogRequests(utc)");
11916 Indent(-1);
11917 WriteLineIndent("}");
11918
11919 // Generate sender methods
11920 WriteLine();
11921 WriteLineIndent("// Send methods");
11922 WriteLine();
11923 WriteLineIndent("/**");
11924 WriteLineIndent(" * Send value");
11925 WriteLineIndent(" * @this {!" + client + "}");
11926 WriteLineIndent(" * @param {!object} value Value to send");
11927 WriteLineIndent(" * @returns {!number} Sent bytes");
11928 WriteLineIndent(" */");
11929 WriteLineIndent("send (value) {");
11930 Indent(1);
11931 if (p->body)
11932 {
11933 for (const auto& s : p->body->structs)
11934 {
11935 if (s->message)
11936 {
11937 WriteLineIndent("if ((value instanceof " + *s->name + ") && (value.fbeType === this." + *s->name + "SenderModel.fbeType)) {");
11938 Indent(1);
11939 WriteLineIndent("return this.send_" + *s->name + "(value)");
11940 Indent(-1);
11941 WriteLineIndent("}");
11942 }
11943 }
11944 }
11945 if (p->import)
11946 {
11947 WriteLineIndent("let result = 0");
11948 for (const auto& import : p->import->imports)
11949 {
11950 WriteLineIndent("result = this._" + *import + "Client.send(value)");
11951 WriteLineIndent("if (result > 0) {");
11952 Indent(1);
11953 WriteLineIndent("return result");
11954 Indent(-1);
11955 WriteLineIndent("}");
11956 }
11957 }
11958 WriteLineIndent("return 0");
11959 Indent(-1);
11960 WriteLineIndent("}");
11961 if (p->body)
11962 {
11963 for (const auto& s : p->body->structs)
11964 {
11965 if (s->message)
11966 {
11967 WriteLine();
11968 WriteLineIndent("/**");
11969 WriteLineIndent(" * Send " + *s->name + " value");
11970 WriteLineIndent(" * @this {!" + client + "}");
11971 WriteLineIndent(" * @param {!" + *s->name + "} value " + *s->name + " value to send");
11972 WriteLineIndent(" * @returns {!number} Sent bytes");
11973 WriteLineIndent(" */");
11974 WriteLineIndent("send_" + *s->name + " (value) { // eslint-disable-line");
11975 Indent(1);
11976 WriteLineIndent("// Serialize the value into the FBE stream");
11977 WriteLineIndent("let serialized = this." + *s->name + "SenderModel.serialize(value)");
11978 WriteLineIndent("console.assert((serialized > 0), '" + *p->name + "." + *s->name + " serialization failed!')");
11979 WriteLineIndent("console.assert(this." + *s->name + "SenderModel.verify(), '" + *p->name + "." + *s->name + " validation failed!')");
11980 WriteLine();
11981 WriteLineIndent("// Log the value");
11982 WriteLineIndent("if (this.logging) {");
11983 Indent(1);
11984 WriteLineIndent("this.onSendLog(value.toString())");
11985 Indent(-1);
11986 WriteLineIndent("}");
11987 WriteLine();
11988 WriteLineIndent("// Send the serialized value");
11989 WriteLineIndent("return this.sendSerialized(serialized)");
11990 Indent(-1);
11991 WriteLineIndent("}");
11992 }
11993 }
11994 }
11995
11996 // Generate sender message handler
11997 WriteLine();
11998 WriteLineIndent("/**");
11999 WriteLineIndent(" * Send message handler");
12000 WriteLineIndent(" * @this {!" + client + "}");
12001 WriteLineIndent(" * @param {!Uint8Array} buffer Buffer to send");
12002 WriteLineIndent(" * @param {!number} offset Buffer offset");
12003 WriteLineIndent(" * @param {!number} size Buffer size");
12004 WriteLineIndent(" */");
12005 WriteLineIndent("onSend (buffer, offset, size) {");
12006 Indent(1);
12007 WriteLineIndent("console.assert(true, '" + *p->name + ".Client.onSend() not implemented!')");
12008 WriteLineIndent("debugger // eslint-disable-line");
12009 WriteLineIndent("return 0");
12010 Indent(-1);
12011 WriteLineIndent("}");
12012
12013 // Generate setup send message handler
12014 WriteLine();
12015 WriteLineIndent("/**");
12016 WriteLineIndent(" * Setup send message handler");
12017 WriteLineIndent(" * @this {!" + client + "}");
12018 WriteLineIndent(" * @param {!function} handler Send message handler");
12019 WriteLineIndent(" */");
12020 WriteLineIndent("set onSendHandler (handler) { // eslint-disable-line");
12021 Indent(1);
12022 WriteLineIndent("this.onSend = handler");
12023 if (p->import)
12024 {
12025 for (const auto& import : p->import->imports)
12026 WriteLineIndent("this._" + *import + "Client.onSendHandler = handler");
12027 }
12028 Indent(-1);
12029 WriteLineIndent("}");
12030
12031 // Generate setup send log message handler
12032 WriteLine();
12033 WriteLineIndent("/**");
12034 WriteLineIndent(" * Setup send log message handler");
12035 WriteLineIndent(" * @this {!" + client + "}");
12036 WriteLineIndent(" * @param {!function} handler Send log message handler");
12037 WriteLineIndent(" */");
12038 WriteLineIndent("set onSendLogHandler (handler) { // eslint-disable-line");
12039 Indent(1);
12040 WriteLineIndent("this.onSendLog = handler");
12041 if (p->import)
12042 {
12043 for (const auto& import : p->import->imports)
12044 WriteLineIndent("this._" + *import + "Client.onSendLogHandler = handler");
12045 }
12046 Indent(-1);
12047 WriteLineIndent("}");
12048
12049 // Generate receiver handlers
12050 if (p->body)
12051 {
12052 WriteLine();
12053 WriteLineIndent("// Receive handlers");
12054 for (const auto& s : p->body->structs)
12055 {
12056 if (s->message)
12057 {
12058 WriteLine();
12059 WriteLineIndent("/**");
12060 WriteLineIndent(" * " + *s->name + " receive handler");
12061 WriteLineIndent(" * @this {!" + client + "}");
12062 WriteLineIndent(" * @param {!" + *s->name + "} value " + *s->name + " received value");
12063 WriteLineIndent(" */");
12064 WriteLineIndent("onReceive_" + *s->name + " (value) {} // eslint-disable-line");
12065 }
12066 }
12067 WriteLine();
12068 }
12069
12070 // Generate receiver message handler
12071 WriteLineIndent("/**");
12072 WriteLineIndent(" * " + *p->name + " receive message handler");
12073 WriteLineIndent(" * @this {!" + client + "}");
12074 WriteLineIndent(" * @param {!number} type Message type");
12075 WriteLineIndent(" * @param {!Uint8Array} buffer Buffer to send");
12076 WriteLineIndent(" * @param {!number} offset Buffer offset");
12077 WriteLineIndent(" * @param {!number} size Buffer size");
12078 WriteLineIndent(" * @returns {!boolean} Success flag");
12079 WriteLineIndent(" */");
12080 WriteLineIndent("onReceive (type, buffer, offset, size) {");
12081 Indent(1);
12082 if (p->body)
12083 {
12084 WriteLineIndent("switch (type) {");
12085 Indent(1);
12086 for (const auto& s : p->body->structs)
12087 {
12088 if (s->message)
12089 {
12090 WriteLineIndent("case " + *s->name + model + ".fbeType: {");
12091 Indent(1);
12092 WriteLineIndent("// Deserialize the value from the FBE stream");
12093 WriteLineIndent("this._" + *s->name + "ReceiverModel.attachBuffer(buffer, offset)");
12094 WriteLineIndent("console.assert(this._" + *s->name + "ReceiverModel.verify(), '" + *p->name + "." + *s->name + " validation failed!')");
12095 WriteLineIndent("let deserialized = this._" + *s->name + "ReceiverModel.deserialize(this._" + *s->name + "ReceiverValue)");
12096 WriteLineIndent("console.assert((deserialized.size > 0), '" + *p->name + "." + *s->name + " deserialization failed!')");
12097 WriteLine();
12098 WriteLineIndent("// Log the value");
12099 WriteLineIndent("if (this.logging) {");
12100 Indent(1);
12101 WriteLineIndent("this.onReceiveLog(this._" + *s->name + "ReceiverValue.toString())");
12102 Indent(-1);
12103 WriteLineIndent("}");
12104 WriteLine();
12105 WriteLineIndent("// Call receive handler with deserialized value");
12106 WriteLineIndent("this.onReceive_" + *s->name + "(this._" + *s->name + "ReceiverValue)");
12107 WriteLineIndent("return true");
12108 Indent(-1);
12109 WriteLineIndent("}");
12110 }
12111 }
12112 WriteLineIndent("default: break");
12113 Indent(-1);
12114 WriteLineIndent("}");
12115 }
12116 if (p->import)
12117 {
12118 WriteLine();
12119 for (const auto& import : p->import->imports)
12120 {
12121 WriteLineIndent("// noinspection RedundantIfStatementJS");
12122 WriteLineIndent("if ((this." + *import + "Client != null) && this." + *import + "Client.onReceive(type, buffer, offset, size)) {");
12123 Indent(1);
12124 WriteLineIndent("return true");
12125 Indent(-1);
12126 WriteLineIndent("}");
12127 }
12128 WriteLine();
12129 }
12130 WriteLineIndent("return false");
12131 Indent(-1);
12132 WriteLineIndent("}");
12133
12134 // Generate setup receive log message handler
12135 WriteLine();
12136 WriteLineIndent("/**");
12137 WriteLineIndent(" * Setup receive log message handler");
12138 WriteLineIndent(" * @this {!" + client + "}");
12139 WriteLineIndent(" * @param {!function} handler Receive log message handler");
12140 WriteLineIndent(" */");
12141 WriteLineIndent("set onReceiveLogHandler (handler) { // eslint-disable-line");
12142 Indent(1);
12143 WriteLineIndent("this.onReceiveLog = handler");
12144 if (p->import)
12145 {
12146 for (const auto& import : p->import->imports)
12147 WriteLineIndent("this._" + *import + "Client.onReceiveLogHandler = handler");
12148 }
12149 Indent(-1);
12150 WriteLineIndent("}");
12151
12152 // Generate request methods
12153 WriteLine();
12154 WriteLineIndent("// Request methods");
12155
12156 // Generate request value method
12157 WriteLine();
12158 WriteLineIndent("/**");
12159 WriteLineIndent(" * Request value");
12160 WriteLineIndent(" * @this {!" + client + "}");
12161 WriteLineIndent(" * @param {!object} value Value to request");
12162 WriteLineIndent(" * @param {!number} timeout Timeout in milliseconds (default is 0)");
12163 WriteLineIndent(" * @returns {Promise} Response promise");
12164 WriteLineIndent(" */");
12165 WriteLineIndent("request (value, timeout = 0) {");
12166 Indent(1);
12167 WriteLineIndent("let promise = new fbe.DeferredPromise()");
12168 WriteLineIndent("let current = Date.now()");
12169 WriteLine();
12170 WriteLineIndent("// Send the request message");
12171 WriteLineIndent("let serialized = this.send(value)");
12172 WriteLineIndent("if (serialized > 0) {");
12173 Indent(1);
12174 WriteLineIndent("// Calculate the unique timestamp");
12175 WriteLineIndent("this._timestamp = (current <= this._timestamp) ? this._timestamp + 1 : current");
12176 WriteLine();
12177 WriteLineIndent("// Register the request");
12178 WriteLineIndent("this._requests_by_id.set(value.id, [this._timestamp, timeout, promise])");
12179 WriteLineIndent("if (timeout > 0) {");
12180 Indent(1);
12181 WriteLineIndent("this._requests_by_timestamp.set(this._timestamp, value.id)");
12182 Indent(-1);
12183 WriteLineIndent("}");
12184 Indent(-1);
12185 WriteLineIndent("} else {");
12186 Indent(1);
12187 WriteLineIndent("promise.reject(new Error('Send request failed!'))");
12188 Indent(-1);
12189 WriteLineIndent("}");
12190 WriteLine();
12191 WriteLineIndent("return promise");
12192 Indent(-1);
12193 WriteLineIndent("}");
12194
12195 // Generate response value method
12196 WriteLine();
12197 WriteLineIndent("/**");
12198 WriteLineIndent(" * Response value");
12199 WriteLineIndent(" * @this {!" + client + "}");
12200 WriteLineIndent(" * @param {!object} value Value to response");
12201 WriteLineIndent(" * @returns {!boolean} Response handle flag");
12202 WriteLineIndent(" */");
12203 WriteLineIndent("response (value) {");
12204 Indent(1);
12205 WriteLineIndent("let item = this._requests_by_id.get(value.id)");
12206 WriteLineIndent("if (item != null) {");
12207 Indent(1);
12208 WriteLineIndent("let timestamp = item[0]");
12209 WriteLineIndent("let promise = item[2]");
12210 WriteLineIndent("promise.resolve(value)");
12211 WriteLineIndent("this._requests_by_id.delete(value.id)");
12212 WriteLineIndent("this._requests_by_timestamp.delete(timestamp)");
12213 WriteLineIndent("return true");
12214 Indent(-1);
12215 WriteLineIndent("}");
12216 if (p->import)
12217 {
12218 WriteLine();
12219 for (const auto& import : p->import->imports)
12220 {
12221 WriteLineIndent("// noinspection RedundantIfStatementJS");
12222 WriteLineIndent("if (this._" + *import + "Client.response(value)) {");
12223 Indent(1);
12224 WriteLineIndent("return true");
12225 Indent(-1);
12226 WriteLineIndent("}");
12227 }
12228 WriteLine();
12229 }
12230 WriteLineIndent("return false");
12231 Indent(-1);
12232 WriteLineIndent("}");
12233
12234 // Generate reject value method
12235 WriteLine();
12236 WriteLineIndent("/**");
12237 WriteLineIndent(" * Reject value");
12238 WriteLineIndent(" * @this {!" + client + "}");
12239 WriteLineIndent(" * @param {!object} value Value to reject");
12240 WriteLineIndent(" * @returns {!boolean} Reject handle flag");
12241 WriteLineIndent(" */");
12242 WriteLineIndent("reject (value) {");
12243 Indent(1);
12244 WriteLineIndent("let item = this._requests_by_id.get(value.id)");
12245 WriteLineIndent("if (item != null) {");
12246 Indent(1);
12247 WriteLineIndent("let timestamp = item[0]");
12248 WriteLineIndent("let promise = item[2]");
12249 WriteLineIndent("promise.reject(value)");
12250 WriteLineIndent("this._requests_by_id.delete(value.id)");
12251 WriteLineIndent("this._requests_by_timestamp.delete(timestamp)");
12252 WriteLineIndent("return true");
12253 Indent(-1);
12254 WriteLineIndent("}");
12255 if (p->import)
12256 {
12257 WriteLine();
12258 for (const auto& import : p->import->imports)
12259 {
12260 WriteLineIndent("// noinspection RedundantIfStatementJS");
12261 WriteLineIndent("if (this._" + *import + "Client.reject(value)) {");
12262 Indent(1);
12263 WriteLineIndent("return true");
12264 Indent(-1);
12265 WriteLineIndent("}");
12266 }
12267 WriteLine();
12268 }
12269 WriteLineIndent("return false");
12270 Indent(-1);
12271 WriteLineIndent("}");
12272
12273 // Generate reset client requests method
12274 WriteLine();
12275 WriteLineIndent("/**");
12276 WriteLineIndent(" * Reset client requests");
12277 WriteLineIndent(" * @this {!" + client + "}");
12278 WriteLineIndent(" */");
12279 WriteLineIndent("resetRequests () {");
12280 Indent(1);
12281 if (p->import)
12282 {
12283 for (const auto& import : p->import->imports)
12284 WriteLineIndent("this._" + *import + "Client.resetRequests()");
12285 WriteLine();
12286 }
12287 WriteLineIndent("for (let [, value] of this._requests_by_id) {");
12288 Indent(1);
12289 WriteLineIndent("value[2].reject(new Error('Reset client!'))");
12290 Indent(-1);
12291 WriteLineIndent("}");
12292 WriteLineIndent("this._requests_by_id.clear()");
12293 WriteLineIndent("this._requests_by_timestamp.clear()");
12294 Indent(-1);
12295 WriteLineIndent("}");
12296
12297 // Generate watchdog client requests method
12298 WriteLine();
12299 WriteLineIndent("/**");
12300 WriteLineIndent(" * Watchdog client requests for timeouts");
12301 WriteLineIndent(" * @this {!" + client + "}");
12302 WriteLineIndent(" * @param {!number} utc UTC timestamp in milliseconds");
12303 WriteLineIndent(" */");
12304 WriteLineIndent("watchdogRequests (utc) {");
12305 Indent(1);
12306 if (p->import)
12307 {
12308 for (const auto& import : p->import->imports)
12309 WriteLineIndent("this._" + *import + "Client.watchdogRequests(utc)");
12310 WriteLine();
12311 }
12312 WriteLineIndent("for (let [, value] of this._requests_by_timestamp) {");
12313 Indent(1);
12314 WriteLineIndent("let item = this._requests_by_id.get(value)");
12315 WriteLineIndent("let id = value");
12316 WriteLineIndent("let timestamp = item[0]");
12317 WriteLineIndent("let timespan = item[1]");
12318 WriteLineIndent("if ((timestamp + timespan) <= utc) {");
12319 Indent(1);
12320 WriteLineIndent("let promise = item[2]");
12321 WriteLineIndent("promise.reject(new Error('Timeout!'))");
12322 WriteLineIndent("this._requests_by_id.delete(id)");
12323 WriteLineIndent("this._requests_by_timestamp.delete(timestamp)");
12324 Indent(-1);
12325 WriteLineIndent("}");
12326 Indent(-1);
12327 WriteLineIndent("}");
12328 Indent(-1);
12329 WriteLineIndent("}");
12330
12331 // Generate client end
12332 Indent(-1);
12333 WriteLineIndent("}");
12334
12335 // Generate client exports
12336 WriteLine();
12337 WriteLineIndent("exports." + client + " = " + client);
12338}
12339
12340bool GeneratorJavaScript::IsPrimitiveType(const std::string& type)
12341{
12342 return ((type == "bool") || (type == "byte") ||
12343 (type == "char") || (type == "wchar") ||
12344 (type == "int8") || (type == "uint8") ||
12345 (type == "int16") || (type == "uint16") ||
12346 (type == "int32") || (type == "uint32") ||
12347 (type == "int64") || (type == "uint64") ||
12348 (type == "float") || (type == "double"));
12349}
12350
12351bool GeneratorJavaScript::IsJavaScriptType(const std::string& type)
12352{
12353 return IsPrimitiveType(type) || (type == "bytes") || (type == "string") || (type == "timestamp");
12354}
12355
12356std::string GeneratorJavaScript::ConvertEnumSize(const std::string& type)
12357{
12358 if (type == "byte")
12359 return "1";
12360 else if (type == "char")
12361 return "1";
12362 else if (type == "wchar")
12363 return "4";
12364 else if (type == "int8")
12365 return "1";
12366 else if (type == "uint8")
12367 return "1";
12368 else if (type == "int16")
12369 return "2";
12370 else if (type == "uint16")
12371 return "2";
12372 else if (type == "int32")
12373 return "4";
12374 else if (type == "uint32")
12375 return "4";
12376 else if (type == "int64")
12377 return "8";
12378 else if (type == "uint64")
12379 return "8";
12380
12381 yyerror("Unsupported enum base type - " + type);
12382 return "";
12383}
12384
12385std::string GeneratorJavaScript::ConvertEnumType(const std::string& type)
12386{
12387 if (type == "byte")
12388 return "Byte";
12389 else if (type == "char")
12390 return "UInt8";
12391 else if (type == "wchar")
12392 return "UInt32";
12393 else if (type == "int8")
12394 return "Int8";
12395 else if (type == "uint8")
12396 return "UInt8";
12397 else if (type == "int16")
12398 return "Int16";
12399 else if (type == "uint16")
12400 return "UInt16";
12401 else if (type == "int32")
12402 return "Int32";
12403 else if (type == "uint32")
12404 return "UInt32";
12405 else if (type == "int64")
12406 return "Int64";
12407 else if (type == "uint64")
12408 return "UInt64";
12409
12410 yyerror("Unsupported enum base type - " + type);
12411 return "";
12412}
12413
12414std::string GeneratorJavaScript::ConvertEnumConstant(const std::string& name, const std::string& type, const std::string& value)
12415{
12416 if (((type == "char") || (type == "wchar")) && CppCommon::StringUtils::StartsWith(value, "'"))
12417 return value + ".charCodeAt(0)";
12418 else if (type == "int64")
12419 return ConvertConstantInt64(value);
12420 else if (type == "uint64")
12421 return ConvertConstantUInt64(value);
12422 else if (type.empty())
12423 {
12424 // Fill flags values
12425 std::vector<std::string> flags = CppCommon::StringUtils::Split(value, '|', true);
12426
12427 // Generate flags combination
12428 if (!flags.empty())
12429 {
12430 std::string result = "";
12431 bool first = true;
12432 for (const auto& it : flags)
12433 {
12434 result += (first ? "" : " | ") + name + "." + CppCommon::StringUtils::ToTrim(it);
12435 first = false;
12436 }
12437 return result;
12438 }
12439 }
12440
12441 return value;
12442}
12443
12444std::string GeneratorJavaScript::ConvertTypeName(const std::string& type, bool optional)
12445{
12446 if (type == "bool")
12447 return "boolean";
12448 else if ((type == "byte") || (type == "int8") || (type == "uint8") || (type == "int16") || (type == "uint16") || (type == "int32") || (type == "uint32") || (type == "int64") || (type == "uint64") || (type == "float") || (type == "double"))
12449 return "number";
12450 else if (type == "decimal")
12451 return "Big";
12452 else if (type == "bytes")
12453 return "Uint8Array";
12454 else if (type == "timestamp")
12455 return "Date";
12456 else if ((type == "char") || (type == "wchar") || (type == "string"))
12457 return "string";
12458 else if (type == "uuid")
12459 return "UUID";
12460
12461 return type;
12462}
12463
12464std::string GeneratorJavaScript::ConvertTypeName(const StructField& field)
12465{
12466 if (field.array)
12467 return "Array";
12468 else if (field.vector)
12469 return "Array";
12470 else if (field.list)
12471 return "Array";
12472 else if (field.set)
12473 return "Set";
12474 else if (field.map)
12475 return "Map";
12476 else if (field.hash)
12477 return "Map";
12478
12479 return ConvertTypeName(*field.type, field.optional);
12480}
12481
12482std::string GeneratorJavaScript::ConvertTypeFieldName(const std::string& type, bool final)
12483{
12484 std::string modelType = final ? "Final" : "Field";
12485
12486 if (type == "bool")
12487 return "fbe." + modelType + "ModelBool";
12488 else if (type == "byte")
12489 return "fbe." + modelType + "ModelByte";
12490 else if (type == "char")
12491 return "fbe." + modelType + "ModelChar";
12492 else if (type == "wchar")
12493 return "fbe." + modelType + "ModelWChar";
12494 else if (type == "int8")
12495 return "fbe." + modelType + "ModelInt8";
12496 else if (type == "uint8")
12497 return "fbe." + modelType + "ModelUInt8";
12498 else if (type == "int16")
12499 return "fbe." + modelType + "ModelInt16";
12500 else if (type == "uint16")
12501 return "fbe." + modelType + "ModelUInt16";
12502 else if (type == "int32")
12503 return "fbe." + modelType + "ModelInt32";
12504 else if (type == "uint32")
12505 return "fbe." + modelType + "ModelUInt32";
12506 else if (type == "int64")
12507 return "fbe." + modelType + "ModelInt64";
12508 else if (type == "uint64")
12509 return "fbe." + modelType + "ModelUInt64";
12510 else if (type == "float")
12511 return "fbe." + modelType + "ModelFloat";
12512 else if (type == "double")
12513 return "fbe." + modelType + "ModelDouble";
12514 else if (type == "decimal")
12515 return "fbe." + modelType + "ModelDecimal";
12516 else if (type == "timestamp")
12517 return "fbe." + modelType + "ModelTimestamp";
12518 else if (type == "uuid")
12519 return "fbe." + modelType + "ModelUUID";
12520 else if (type == "bytes")
12521 return "fbe." + modelType + "ModelBytes";
12522 else if (type == "string")
12523 return "fbe." + modelType + "ModelString";
12524
12525 std::string ns = "";
12526 std::string t = type;
12527
12528 size_t pos = type.find_last_of('.');
12529 if (pos != std::string::npos)
12530 {
12531 ns.assign(type, 0, pos + 1);
12532 t.assign(type, pos + 1, type.size() - pos);
12533 }
12534
12535 return ns + modelType + "Model" + ConvertTypeName(t, false);
12536}
12537
12538std::string GeneratorJavaScript::ConvertTypeFieldDeclaration(const StructField& field, bool final)
12539{
12540 std::string modelType = final ? "Final" : "Field";
12541
12542 if (field.array)
12543 return "fbe." + modelType + "ModelArray";
12544 else if (field.vector || field.list)
12545 return "fbe." + modelType + "ModelVector";
12546 else if (field.set)
12547 return "fbe." + modelType + "ModelSet";
12548 else if (field.map || field.hash)
12549 return "fbe." + modelType + "ModelMap";
12550 else if (field.optional)
12551 return "fbe." + modelType + "ModelOptional";
12552 else
12553 return ConvertTypeFieldName(*field.type, final);
12554}
12555
12556std::string GeneratorJavaScript::ConvertTypeFieldInitialization(const std::string& type, bool optional, const std::string& offset, bool final)
12557{
12558 std::string modelType = final ? "Final" : "Field";
12559
12560 if (optional)
12561 return "fbe." + modelType + "ModelOptional(new " + ConvertTypeFieldInitialization(type, false, offset, final)+ ", buffer, " + offset + ")";
12562 else
12563 return ConvertTypeFieldName(type, final) + "(buffer, " + offset + ")";
12564}
12565
12566std::string GeneratorJavaScript::ConvertTypeFieldInitialization(const StructField& field, const std::string& offset, bool final)
12567{
12568 std::string modelType = final ? "Final" : "Field";
12569
12570 if (field.array)
12571 return "fbe." + modelType + "ModelArray(new " + ConvertTypeFieldInitialization(*field.type, field.optional, offset, final) + ", buffer, " + offset + ", " + std::to_string(field.N) + ")";
12572 else if (field.vector || field.list)
12573 return "fbe." + modelType + "ModelVector(new " + ConvertTypeFieldInitialization(*field.type, field.optional, offset, final) + ", buffer, " + offset + ")";
12574 else if (field.set)
12575 return "fbe." + modelType + "ModelSet(new " + ConvertTypeFieldInitialization(*field.type, field.optional, offset, final) + ", buffer, " + offset + ")";
12576 else if (field.map || field.hash)
12577 return "fbe." + modelType + "ModelMap(new " + ConvertTypeFieldInitialization(*field.key, false, offset, final) + ", new " + ConvertTypeFieldInitialization(*field.type, field.optional, offset, final) + ", buffer, " + offset + ")";
12578 else
12579 return ConvertTypeFieldInitialization(*field.type, field.optional, offset, final);
12580}
12581
12582std::string GeneratorJavaScript::ConvertConstant(const std::string& type, const std::string& value, bool optional)
12583{
12584 if (value == "true")
12585 return "true";
12586 else if (value == "false")
12587 return "false";
12588 else if (value == "null")
12589 return "undefined";
12590 else if (value == "min")
12591 {
12592 if ((type == "byte") || (type == "uint8") || (type == "uint16") || (type == "uint32"))
12593 return "0";
12594 else if (type == "int8")
12595 return "-128";
12596 else if (type == "int16")
12597 return "-32768";
12598 else if (type == "int32")
12599 return "-2147483648";
12600 else if (type == "int64")
12601 return ConvertConstantInt64("-9223372036854775808");
12602 else if (type == "uint64")
12603 return ConvertConstantUInt64("0");
12604
12605 yyerror("Unsupported type " + type + " for 'min' constant");
12606 return "";
12607 }
12608 else if (value == "max")
12609 {
12610 if (type == "byte")
12611 return "255";
12612 else if (type == "int8")
12613 return "127";
12614 else if (type == "uint8")
12615 return "255";
12616 else if (type == "int16")
12617 return "32767";
12618 else if (type == "uint16")
12619 return "65535";
12620 else if (type == "int32")
12621 return "2147483647";
12622 else if (type == "uint32")
12623 return "4294967295";
12624 else if (type == "int64")
12625 return ConvertConstantInt64("9223372036854775807");
12626 else if (type == "uint64")
12627 return ConvertConstantUInt64("18446744073709551615");
12628
12629 yyerror("Unsupported type " + type + " for 'max' constant");
12630 return "";
12631 }
12632 else if (value == "epoch")
12633 return "new Date(0)";
12634 else if (value == "uuid0")
12635 return "UUID.nil()";
12636 else if (value == "uuid1")
12637 return "UUID.sequential()";
12638 else if (value == "uuid4")
12639 return "UUID.random()";
12640 else if (value == "utc")
12641 return "new Date(Date.now())";
12642
12643 if (((type == "char") || (type == "wchar")) && !CppCommon::StringUtils::StartsWith(value, "'"))
12644 return "String.fromCharCode(" + value + ")";
12645 else if (type == "int64")
12646 return ConvertConstantInt64(value);
12647 else if (type == "uint64")
12648 return ConvertConstantUInt64(value);
12649 else if (type == "decimal")
12650 return "new Big('" + value + "')";
12651 else if (type == "string")
12652 return ConvertString(value);
12653 else if (type == "uuid")
12654 return "new UUID(" + ConvertString(value) + ")";
12655
12656 if (IsJavaScriptType(type))
12657 return value;
12658 else
12659 return "new " + ConvertTypeName(type, false) + "(" + value + ")";
12660}
12661
12662std::string GeneratorJavaScript::ConvertConstantInt64(const std::string& value)
12663{
12664 int64_t full = std::strtoll(value.c_str(), nullptr, 0);
12665 int32_t high = (int32_t)(full >> 32);
12666 uint32_t low = (uint32_t)full;
12667 return "new Int64(" + std::to_string(low) + ", " + std::to_string(high) + ")";
12668}
12669
12670std::string GeneratorJavaScript::ConvertConstantUInt64(const std::string& value)
12671{
12672 uint64_t full = std::strtoull(value.c_str(), nullptr, 0);
12673 uint32_t high = (uint32_t)(full >> 32);
12674 uint32_t low = (uint32_t)full;
12675 return "new UInt64(" + std::to_string(low) + ", " + std::to_string(high) + ")";
12676}
12677
12678std::string GeneratorJavaScript::ConvertDefault(const std::string& type)
12679{
12680 if (type == "bool")
12681 return "false";
12682 else if (type == "byte")
12683 return "0";
12684 else if (type == "bytes")
12685 return "new Uint8Array(0)";
12686 else if ((type == "char") || (type == "wchar"))
12687 return "'\\0'";
12688 else if ((type == "int8") || (type == "uint8") || (type == "int16") || (type == "uint16") || (type == "int32") || (type == "uint32"))
12689 return "0";
12690 else if (type == "int64")
12691 return ConvertConstantInt64("0");
12692 else if (type == "uint64")
12693 return ConvertConstantUInt64("0");
12694 else if ((type == "float") || (type == "double"))
12695 return "0.0";
12696 else if (type == "decimal")
12697 return "new Big(0)";
12698 else if (type == "string")
12699 return "''";
12700 else if (type == "timestamp")
12701 return "new Date(0)";
12702 else if (type == "uuid")
12703 return "new UUID()";
12704
12705 return "new " + type + "()";
12706}
12707
12708std::string GeneratorJavaScript::ConvertDefault(const StructField& field)
12709{
12710 if (field.value)
12711 return ConvertConstant(*field.type, *field.value, field.optional);
12712
12713 if (field.array || field.vector || field.list)
12714 return "[]";
12715 else if (field.set)
12716 return "new Set()";
12717 else if (field.map || field.hash)
12718 return "new Map()";
12719 else if (field.optional)
12720 return "undefined";
12721
12722 return ConvertDefault(*field.type);
12723}
12724
12725std::string GeneratorJavaScript::ConvertString(const std::string& value)
12726{
12727 std::string result;
12728
12729 if (CppCommon::StringUtils::StartsWith(value, "\"") && CppCommon::StringUtils::EndsWith(value, "\"") && (value.size() >= 2))
12730 result = value.substr(1, value.size() - 2);
12731 else
12732 result = value;
12733
12734 return "'" + result + "'";
12735}
12736
12737std::string GeneratorJavaScript::ConvertVariable(const std::string& type, const std::string& name, bool optional)
12738{
12739 if ((type == "char") || (type == "wchar"))
12740 return "((" + name + " != null) ? " + name + ".charCodeAt(0) : null)";
12741 else if ((type == "int64") || (type == "uint64"))
12742 return "((" + name + " != null) ? " + name + ".toNumber() : null)";
12743 else if (type == "bytes")
12744 return "((" + name + " != null) ? Buffer.from(" + name + ").toString('base64') : null)";
12745 else if (type == "decimal")
12746 return "((" + name + " != null) ? " + name + ".toFixed() : null)";
12747 else if (type == "timestamp")
12748 return "((" + name + " != null) ? (" + name + ".getTime() * 1000000) : null)";
12749 else if (type == "uuid")
12750 return "((" + name + " != null) ? " + name + ".toString() : null)";
12751 else
12752 return "((" + name + " != null) ? " + name + " : null)";
12753}
12754
12755void GeneratorJavaScript::CopyValueToVariable(const std::string& type, const std::string& name, const std::string& variable, bool optional)
12756{
12757 if ((type == "char") || (type == "wchar"))
12758 {
12759 WriteLineIndent("if ((typeof " + name + " === 'string') || (" + name + " instanceof String)) {");
12760 Indent(1);
12761 WriteLineIndent(variable + " = " + name);
12762 Indent(-1);
12763 WriteLineIndent("} else {");
12764 Indent(1);
12765 WriteLineIndent(variable + " = String.fromCharCode(" + name + ")");
12766 Indent(-1);
12767 WriteLineIndent("}");
12768 }
12769 else if (type == "int64")
12770 WriteLineIndent(variable + " = Int64.fromNumber(" + name + ")");
12771 else if (type == "uint64")
12772 WriteLineIndent(variable + " = UInt64.fromNumber(" + name + ")");
12773 else if (type == "bytes")
12774 {
12775 WriteLineIndent("if (typeof " + name + " === 'string') {");
12776 Indent(1);
12777 WriteLineIndent("// noinspection JSUnresolvedFunction");
12778 WriteLineIndent(variable + " = Uint8Array.from(Buffer.from(" + name + ", 'base64'))");
12779 Indent(-1);
12780 WriteLineIndent("} else {");
12781 Indent(1);
12782 WriteLineIndent(variable + " = Uint8Array.from(" + name + ")");
12783 Indent(-1);
12784 WriteLineIndent("}");
12785 }
12786 else if (type == "decimal")
12787 WriteLineIndent(variable + " = new Big(" + name + ")");
12788 else if (type == "timestamp")
12789 {
12790 WriteLineIndent("if (" + name + " instanceof Date) {");
12791 Indent(1);
12792 WriteLineIndent(variable + " = new Date(" + name + ".getTime())");
12793 Indent(-1);
12794 WriteLineIndent("} else {");
12795 Indent(1);
12796 WriteLineIndent(variable + " = new Date(Math.round(" + name + " / 1000000))");
12797 Indent(-1);
12798 WriteLineIndent("}");
12799 }
12800 else if (type == "uuid")
12801 WriteLineIndent(variable + " = new UUID(" + name + ")");
12802 else if (IsJavaScriptType(type))
12803 WriteLineIndent(variable + " = " + name);
12804 else
12805 WriteLineIndent(variable + " = " + ConvertTypeName(type, false) + ".fromObject(" + name + ")");
12806}
12807
12808void GeneratorJavaScript::WriteOutputStreamType(const std::string& type, const std::string& name, bool optional)
12809{
12810 if (type == "bool")
12811 WriteLineIndent("result += " + name + " ? 'true' : 'false'");
12812 else if (type == "bytes")
12813 WriteLineIndent("result += 'bytes[' + " + name + ".length + ']'");
12814 else if ((type == "char") || (type == "wchar"))
12815 WriteLineIndent("result += \"'\" + " + name + ".toString() + \"'\"");
12816 else if (type == "decimal")
12817 WriteLineIndent("result += " + name + ".toFixed()");
12818 else if ((type == "string") || (type == "uuid"))
12819 WriteLineIndent("result += '\"' + " + name + ".toString() + '\"'");
12820 else if (type == "timestamp")
12821 WriteLineIndent("result += " + name + ".getTime() * 1000000");
12822 else
12823 WriteLineIndent("result += " + name + ".toString()");
12824}
12825
12826void GeneratorJavaScript::WriteOutputStreamValue(const std::string& type, const std::string& name, bool optional, bool separate)
12827{
12828 if (optional || (type == "bytes") || (type == "decimal") || (type == "string") || (type == "timestamp") || (type == "uuid"))
12829 {
12830 WriteLineIndent("if (" + name + " != null) {");
12831 Indent(1);
12832 if (separate)
12833 WriteLineIndent("result += first ? '' : ','");
12834 WriteOutputStreamType(type, name, true);
12835 Indent(-1);
12836 WriteLineIndent("} else {");
12837 Indent(1);
12838 if (separate)
12839 WriteLineIndent("result += first ? '' : ','");
12840 WriteLineIndent("result += 'null'");
12841 Indent(-1);
12842 WriteLineIndent("}");
12843 }
12844 else
12845 {
12846 if (separate)
12847 WriteLineIndent("result += first ? '' : ','");
12848 WriteOutputStreamType(type, name, false);
12849 }
12850}
